%222573%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EMixMedia%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Tincher%2C%20classic%20piqu%C3%A9%20polos%2C%20which%20have%20a%20waffle-like%20texture%2C%20are%20being%20replaced%20by%20fine-knit%20styles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20lot%20of%20great%20replacements%20for%20menswear%20now%2C%20which%20would%20be%20more%20of%20a%20fine-gauge%20knit%20and%20maybe%20a%20cotton-merino%20or%20silk%20blend%20for%20a%20more%20updated%20version%2C%26quot%3B%20Tincher%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ESky-high%20heels%20are%20being%20replaced%20by%20more%20practical%20options.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224716%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20woman%20wearing%20a%20pair%20of%20black%20stilettos%20with%20trousers.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a26d6f82ab5f9757adda1ce%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223537%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EStreetstyleshooters%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EGood%20news%20for%20sore%20feet%3A%20Burnette%20said%20extremely%20high%20heels%20that%20are%20neither%20practical%20nor%20comfortable%20are%20a%20fading%20trend.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20place%20of%20these%2C%20the%20stylist%20recommends%20investing%20in%20a%20quality%20pair%20of%20loafers%20with%20elevated%20details%20like%20suede%2C%20leather%2C%20or%20metallic%20accents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20those%20who%20still%20prefer%20heels%2C%20Tincher%20suggested%20more%20wearable%20styles%20such%20as%20kitten%20heels%2C%20slingbacks%2C%20or%20lower%2C%20pointed-toe%20pumps.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EConsider%20swapping%20neutrals%20for%20pastels%20this%20season.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222832%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20man%20wearing%20a%20cream%20shirt%20and%20cream%20pants.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a26dc242ab5f9757adda1f1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221892%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EMoritz%20Scholz%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20several%20years%20of%20monochromatic%20browns%2C%20creams%2C%20and%20other%20neutral%20tones%20dominating%20office%20wear%2C%20Young%20said%20lighter%20colors%20are%20becoming%20more%20popular.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERight%20now%2C%20she's%20seeing%20more%20pastels%2C%20including%20shades%20like%20butter%20yellow%2C%20mellow%20rose%2C%20and%20cornflower%20blue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGonzalez%20also%20mentioned%20that%20pastel%20blazers%20can%20be%20a%20good%20way%20to%20add%20some%20color%20to%20outfits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EIt's%20time%20to%20put%20away%20your%20chunky%20statement%20necklaces.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221742%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20woman%20wearing%20a%20chunky%20gold%20statement%20necklace.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a26db682e5a80cfe05046c4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221307%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EEdward%20Berthelot%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EGonzalez%20and%20Burnette%20both%20said%20that%20oversized%20statement%20necklaces%20are%20falling%20out%20of%20favor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBurnette%20said%20large%20statement%20necklaces%20feel%20more%20reminiscent%20of%20the%20late%202010s%20than%20of%20current%20office%20fashion.%20In%20their%20place%2C%20Gonzalez%20is%20seeing%20daintier%20necklaces%20worn%20either%20alone%20or%20layered.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foffice-fashion-trends-things-going-out-of-style-summer-2026%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1781178721000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a282695208d75cc7b791bbe%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foffice-fashion-trends-things-going-out-of-style-summer-2026%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22According%20to%20stylists%2C%20natural%20fabrics%20and%20wide-leg%20trousers%20will%20be%20popular%20office%20staples%20this%20summer.%20However%2C%20piqu%C3%A9%20polos%20are%20on%20their%20way%20out.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Cheyenne%20Elwell)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Workers%20are%20spending%20over%206%20hours%20a%20week%20'botsitting'%20AI%2C%20fueling%20job%20frustration%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227236%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20worker%20searching%20for%20fake%20content%20through%20social%20media%20related%20to%20election%20campaigns%20at%20the%20headquarters%20of%20the%20National%20Election%20Commission%20(NEC)%20in%20Gwacheon%20in%20April%202025.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a2a94ff85222d2032e7ba94%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224988%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20new%20Glean%20report%20found%20that%20workers%20spend%20almost%20a%20full%20working%20day%20over%20the%20course%20of%20a%20week%20supervising%20AI.%3Cp%3EJung%20Yeon-je%20%2F%20AFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EWorkers%20are%20spending%206.4%20hours%20a%20week%20%26quot%3Bbotsitting%26quot%3B%20AI%2C%20a%20Glean%20report%20found.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBotsitting%20involves%20feeding%20AI%20context%2C%20debugging%20mistakes%2C%20and%20cleaning%20up%20errors.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt's%20encouraging%20more%20workers%20to%20look%20for%20other%20roles%2C%20researchers%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20is%20supposed%20to%20save%20workers%20time.%20Instead%2C%20some%20employees%20report%20spending%20hours%20every%20week%20cleaning%20up%20after%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20new%20report%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-making-workers-feel-smarter-but-worse-at-their-jobs-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGlean's%20Work%20AI%20Institute%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20produced%20with%20researchers%20from%20universities%20including%20Notre%20Dame%2C%20Stanford%2C%20and%20UC%20Berkeley%2C%20found%20that%20white-collar%20workers%20spend%20an%20average%20of%206.4%20hours%20a%20week%20%26quot%3Bbotsitting%26quot%3B%20AI%20%E2%80%94%20feeding%20it%20context%2C%20checking%20outputs%2C%20debugging%20mistakes%2C%20and%20cleaning%20up%20errors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20researchers%20surveyed%206%2C000%20full-time%20workers%20in%20the%20US%2C%20UK%2C%20and%20Australia%20who%20primarily%20work%20on%20computers%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3Eor%20digital%20tools%C2%A0between%20December%202025%20and%20January%202026.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20term%20%26quot%3Bbotsitting%26quot%3B%20was%20coined%20by%20the%20report's%20authors%20to%20describe%20the%20often-overlooked%20work%20required%20to%20make%20AI%20useful.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWorkers%20now%20burn%20an%20average%20of%206.4%20hours%20a%20week%20botsitting%20%E2%80%94%20most%20of%20a%20full%20working%20day%2C%20every%20week%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221c993ece-908f-4bf7-8fef-842cc09d9a41%5C%22%3E'Often%20tedious'%20and%20'exhausting'%20work%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20findings%20highlight%20a%20growing%20disconnect%20between%20individual%20productivity%20gains%20and%20companywide%20performance%20%E2%80%94%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcompanies-waiting-ai-productivity-boom-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eproductivity%20paradox%3C%2Fa%3E%20many%20companies%20are%20facing%2C%20Business%20Insider's%20Juliana%20Kaplan%20and%20Jacob%20Zinkula%20reported%20this%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%2087%25%20of%20workers%20surveyed%20in%20Glean's%20report%20said%20they%20use%20AI%20at%20work%20and%2075%25%20said%20it%20makes%20them%20more%20productive%2C%20only%2013%25%20said%20their%20organization%20was%20performing%20significantly%20better%20because%20of%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Rebecca%20Hinds%2C%20head%20of%20the%20Work%20AI%20Institute%20at%20Glean%20and%20one%20of%20the%20report's%20authors%2C%20much%20of%20the%20missing%20productivity%20is%20being%20consumed%20by%20work%20employees%20never%20expected%20to%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20%26quot%3BCognitive%20Revolution%26quot%3B%20podcast%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20Hinds%20described%20botsitting%20as%20%26quot%3Boften%20tedious%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-automating-boring-work-killing-creativity-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%26quot%3Bexhausting%26quot%3B%20work%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20is%20%26quot%3Bnot%20rewarded%20and%20it's%20not%20appreciated%20or%20tracked%20or%20measured%20and%20certainly%20not%20incentivized%20within%20the%20organization.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22947f51c0-044b-4e48-815c-9fbf59ea5614%5C%22%3EThe%20exit%20risk%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20burden%20appears%20to%20be%20taking%20a%20toll%20on%20employee%20morale.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20found%20that%20workers%20who%20spend%20an%20unusually%20large%20share%20of%20their%20AI%20time%20botsitting%20are%2073%25%20more%20likely%20to%20be%20actively%20looking%20for%20another%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWorkers%20who%20absorb%20it%20without%20recognition%20or%20reward%20grow%20exhausted.%20Then%20they%20grow%20resentful.%20Then%20they%20start%20polishing%20their%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9s%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20report%2C%20the%20frustration%20goes%20beyond%20the%20extra%20work.%20Many%20employees%20now%20spend%20their%20time%20moving%20information%20between%20disconnected%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsatya-nadella-microsoft-how-to-manage-ai-agents-human-employees-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%20systems%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20fixing%20mistakes%2C%20and%20providing%20context%20that%20the%20tools%20should%20already%20have%20%E2%80%94%20effectively%20becoming%20the%20go-between%20for%20technologies%20that%20don't%20work%20well%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20some%20cases%2C%20workers%20are%20also%20being%20asked%20to%20automate%20the%20parts%20of%20their%20jobs%20they%20enjoy%20most%2C%20Hinds%20said%20on%20the%20podcast%2C%20pointing%20to%20customer-service%20employees%20who%20enjoy%20building%20relationships%20but%20are%20increasingly%20expected%20to%20supervise%20AI%20agents%20instead.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20what%20gives%20you%20joy%20and%20meaning%20at%20work%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BThat%20is%20very%20dangerous.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2207a5fca5-86a6-4736-be6e-8b78f7164844%5C%22%3EBreaking%20the%20botsitting%20cycle%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20solution%20isn't%20simply%20to%20deploy%20more%20AI%2C%20according%20to%20researchers.%20The%20organizations%20seeing%20the%20biggest%20gains%20are%20often%20the%20ones%20doing%20more%20work%20around%20AI%20%E2%80%94%20helping%20employees%20access%20the%20right%20context%2C%20teaching%20them%20how%20to%20use%20the%20technology%20effectively%2C%20and%20establishing%20clearer%20standards%20for%20what%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-agents-save-hours-consultant-steps-efficient-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Egood%20AI-assisted%20work%3C%2Fa%3E%20looks%20like.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20companies%20pulling%20ahead%20are%20doing%20something%20different%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20aren't%20spending%20a%20greater%20share%20of%20their%20AI%20time%20using%20AI.%20They're%20spending%20a%20greater%20share%20on%20the%20work%20around%20it%3A%20setting%20context%2C%20defining%20what%20'good'%20looks%20like%2C%20building%20judgment%2C%20and%20deciding%20what%20should%20never%20have%20been%20handed%20to%20a%20model%20in%20the%20first%20place.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20alternative%2C%20the%20authors%20warned%2C%20is%20continuing%20to%20pay%20the%20price%20in%20botsitting%2C%20and%20%26quot%3Bin%20the%20steady%20departure%20of%20the%20people%20who%20got%20tired%20of%20cleaning%20up%20after%20the%20bots.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbotsitting-ai-hidden-human-labor-at-work-2026-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1781178488000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a2a951a85222d2032e7ba95%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbotsitting-ai-hidden-human-labor-at-work-2026-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Workers%20are%20spending%20an%20average%20of%206.4%20hours%20a%20week%20%E2%80%94%20almost%20a%20full%20working%20day%20%E2%80%94%20%26quot%3Bbotsitting%26quot%3B%20AI%2C%20pushing%20some%20to%20look%20for%20an%20exit%2C%20researchers%20say.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22tspirlet%40insider.com%20(Thibault%20Spirlet)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%222%20Days%20After%2030%20Deaths%2C%2016%20Killed%20As%20Forces%20Open%20Fire%20On%20Protesters%20In%20PoK%22%2C%22content%22%3A%222%20Days%20After%2030%20Deaths%2C%2016%20Killed%20As%20Forces%20Open%20Fire%20On%20Protesters%20In%20PoK%22%2C%22published%22%3A1781177993000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2026-06%2Fdd6ohgqo_pok-protest-_650x400_11_June_26.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2F2-days-after-30-deaths-16-killed-as-forces-open-fire-on-protesters-in-pok-11622541%23publisher%3Dnewsstand%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%222%20Days%20After%2030%20Deaths%2C%2016%20Killed%20As%20Forces%20Open%20Fire%20On%20Protesters%20In%20PoK%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Meenakshi%20Natarajan%20row%20ends%20in%20BJP%E2%80%99s%203-0%20Rajya%20Sabha%20sweep%2