ow%2F131657807.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F131657807.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EProducer%20Edida%20Raja%20revealed%20how%20his%20father%2C%20the%20late%20Edida%20Nageswara%20Rao%2C%20influenced%20the%20climax%20of%20the%201981%20hit%20'Seethakoka%20Chiluka'.%20Originally%20a%20tragic%20ending%2C%20it%20was%20changed%20to%20a%20hopeful%20one%20to%20better%20reflect%20the%20inter-caste%20love%20story%2C%20encouraging%20positive%20messages.%20Bharathiraja%20readily%20agreed%20to%20reshoot%2C%20leading%20to%20the%20film's%20immense%20success%20and%20accolades.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Coram%20raised%20%2435%20million%20to%20turn%20security%20cameras%20into%20AI%20detectives%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224160%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Coram%20AI%20cofounders%20Ashesh%20Jain%20and%20Peter%20Ondruska%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a29cb5165e506aa9708d950%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222304%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECoram%20AI%20cofounders%20Ashesh%20Jain%20and%20Peter%20Ondruska%3Cp%3ECoram%20AI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ECoram%20AI%20raised%20%2435%20million%2C%20bringing%20its%20total%20funding%20to%20%2466%20million.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EMore%20than%201%2C500%20sites%20use%20Coram%2C%20including%20Hershey's%20Ice%20Cream%20and%20school%20districts.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ECEO%20Ashesh%20Jain%20said%20Coram%20could%20eventually%20work%20with%20robot%20dogs%20and%20humanoids.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20security%20cameras%20are%20useful%20only%20after%20something%20has%20gone%20wrong.%20Coram%20AI%20wants%20to%20change%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Bay%20Area%20startup%20has%20raised%20%2435%20million%20in%20Series%20B%20funding%20to%20expand%20its%20AI-powered%20physical%20security%20platform%2C%20bringing%20its%20total%20capital%20raised%20to%20%2466%20million.%20The%20round%20was%20co-led%20by%20Ansa%20Capital%20and%20Battery%20Ventures%2C%20with%20participation%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2FUP.Partners%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUP.Partners%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%208VC%2C%20and%20Mosaic%20Ventures.%20The%20company%20declined%20to%20share%20its%20valuation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFounded%20in%202022%2C%20Coram%20helps%20organizations%20use%20the%20security%20equipment%20they%20already%20have.%20It%20connects%20cameras%2C%20badge%20readers%2C%20visitor%20logs%2C%20and%20emergency%20systems%2C%20and%20uses%20AI%20to%20help%20security%20teams%20find%20incidents%20and%20respond%20faster.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECoram%20is%20one%20example%20of%20a%20startup%20riding%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsilicon-valleys-new-slogan-lets-get-physical-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eboom%20in%20physical%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20category%20built%20around%20bringing%20AI%20into%20systems%20that%20act%20in%20the%20real%20world.%20Venture%20capital%20investment%20in%20global%20robotics%20and%20physical%20AI%20has%20grown%20from%20around%20%244%20billion%20in%202019%20to%20%2426%20billion%20in%202025%2C%20according%20to%20PitchBook%20data.%20So%20far%20this%20year%2C%20companies%20in%20the%20space%20have%20raised%20more%20than%20%2423%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECoram%20was%20cofounded%20by%20Ashesh%20Jain%2C%20who%20previously%20led%20autonomy%20at%20Lyft's%20self-driving%20division%20and%20worked%20as%20an%20engineering%20leader%20at%20Zoox%2C%20and%20Peter%20Ondruska%2C%20who%20led%20AI%20research%20at%20Lyft%20and%20Toyota's%20Woven%20division%20after%20Toyota%20acquired%20Lyft's%20self-driving%20technology%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20spending%20years%20building%20AI%20systems%20for%20autonomous%20vehicles%2C%20Jain%20and%20Ondruska%20figured%20they%20could%20apply%20their%20expertise%20to%20an%20even%20bigger%20market%3A%20physical%20security.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20earlier%20mission%20was%20to%20protect%20every%20public%20road%2C%20and%20now%20it%20is%20to%20protect%20every%20physical%20space%2C%26quot%3B%20Jain%2C%20Coram's%20CEO%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECoram%20is%20competing%20in%20a%20crowded%20security%20market%20that%20has%20also%20drawn%20scrutiny.%20Verkada%2C%20valued%20at%20%245.8%20billion%2C%20suffered%20a%20major%20breach%20in%202021%20when%20hackers%20accessed%20more%20than%20150%2C000%20live%20customer%20cameras%2C%20including%20inside%20hospitals%20and%20schools.%20Other%20competitors%20include%20Motorola%20Solutions'%20Avigilon%20and%20Eagle%20Eye%20Networks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJain%20said%20Coram%20is%20racing%20to%20meet%20customer%20demand.%20Since%20raising%20its%20%2413.8%20million%20Series%20A%20last%20year%2C%20Jain%20said%20the%20company's%20revenue%20has%20grown%20fourfold%2C%20and%20its%20customer%20base%20has%20tripled.%20The%20startup%20will%20use%20the%20new%20funds%20to%20expand%20its%20sales%20team%20and%20invest%20in%20product%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMore%20than%201%2C500%20sites%20across%20the%20US%20and%20Canada%20use%20Coram%2C%20Jain%20said%2C%20including%20Hershey's%20Ice%20Cream%2C%20Lakepointe%20Church%2C%20which%20has%20eight%20campuses%20in%20Dallas%2C%20and%20the%20junk%20removal%20company%201-800-GOT-JUNK%3F.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20startup%20has%20found%20particular%20traction%20with%20school%20districts.%20Jain%20said%20Coram%20can%20detect%20a%20firearm%2C%20automatically%20alert%20911%2C%20and%20help%20trigger%20a%20campus%20lockdown.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20is%20also%20rolling%20out%20a%20new%20product%20called%20Deep%20Investigation.%20The%20tool%20lets%20customers%20ask%20questions%20of%20the%20security%20platform%20and%20can%20be%20accessed%20through%20tools%20like%20ChatGPT%20or%20Claude%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20Jain%20said%20a%20school%20could%20ask%20Coram%20to%20find%20every%20fight%20on%20campus%20over%20the%20past%20month%2C%20identify%20patterns%2C%20pull%20clips%20with%20student%20faces%20blurred%2C%20and%20generate%20a%20report.%20A%20warehouse%20customer%20could%20ask%20how%20long%20trucks%20are%20parked%20at%20loading%20docks%20or%20when%20a%20facility%20is%20busiest.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJain%20said%20the%20goal%20is%20to%20give%20customers%20the%20equivalent%20of%20a%20sophisticated%20data%20science%20team%2C%20answering%20in%20minutes%20questions%20that%20would%20otherwise%20require%20more%20staff%20and%20hours%20of%20manual%20review.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECoram%20impressed%20some%20investors%20by%20showing%20off%20its%20technology%20during%20the%20fundraising%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2FUP.Partners%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUP.Partners%3C%2Fa%3E'%20Ally%20Warson%2C%20an%20investor%20in%20the%20latest%20round%2C%20visited%20Coram's%20Sunnyvale%20office%2C%20the%20startup%20had%20its%20software%20running%20on%20the%20security%20cameras%20as%20her%20team%20walked%20in.%20Jain%20then%20invited%20Warson%20to%20ask%20the%20software%20questions%20in%20any%20language.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20told%20the%20product%20in%20French%20to%20pull%20up%20all%20the%20people%20who%20had%20entered%20the%20office%20that%20morning%20wearing%20white%20shoes%20with%20a%20blue%20stripe%2C%26quot%3B%20Warson%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20we%20watched%20it%20translate%20the%20French%20into%20English%2C%20and%20pull%20up%20photos%20of%20us%20entering%20the%20office.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECoram's%20ambition%20is%20to%20become%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20security%20providers%20in%20the%20world.%20Jain%20envisions%20a%20future%20in%20which%20Coram's%20software%20works%20with%20robot%20dogs%20and%20potentially%20humanoids%20to%20help%20protect%20properties.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEvery%20building%20will%20have%20robotic%20security%2C%26quot%3B%20Jain%20said.%20%26quot%3BThat%20is%20a%20part%20of%20our%20mission.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcoram-turn-security-cameras-into-ai-detectives-2026-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1781177401000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a29cb85b8e3cbc12bcaf828%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcoram-turn-security-cameras-into-ai-detectives-2026-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20security%20company%20works%20with%20existing%20cameras%20today%2C%20but%20Coram's%20CEO%20sees%20robot%20dogs%20and%20humanoids%20as%20part%20of%20the%20startup's%20future.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22rjetha%40insider.com%20(Rya%20Jetha)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Brother%2C%20Mother%20Kill%20Woman%20Over%20Her%20Relationship%20In%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20Arrested%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22Political%20parties%20have%20described%20the%20incident%20as%20a%20possible%20honour%20killing%20and%20urged%20the%20government%20to%20enact%20a%20special%20law%20to%20prevent%20such%20crimes.%22%2C%22published%22%3A1781177096000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2026-06%2Fp1182mr4_tamil-nadu_625x300_11_June_26.jpg%3Fim%3DFitAndFill%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1280%2Cheight%3D720%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fman-his-mother-arrested-for-killing-sister-in-tamil-nadu-over-instagram-love-11622511%23publisher%3Dnewsstand%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Political%20parties%20have%20described%20the%20incident%20as%20a%20possible%20honour%20killing%20and%20urged%20the%20government%20to%20enact%20a%20special%20law%20to%20prevent%20such%20crimes.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia