-131657281%2Cimgsize-27434.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fi-want-three-more-people-in-the-room-shahid-kapoor-opens-up-about-the-big-change-he-made-after-oromeo-and-devas-failure%2Farticleshow%2F131657281.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F131657281.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EAmid%20promotions%20for%20'Cocktail%202'%2C%20Shahid%20Kapoor%20revealed%20that%20following%20the%20failure%20of%20'O'Romeo'%20and%20'Deva'%2C%20he%20no%20longer%20attends%20script%20narrations%20alone.%20Speaking%20to%20The%20Hollywood%20Reporter%20India%2C%20he%20said%20films%20are%20%26quot%3Bextremely%20unpredictable%26quot%3B%20and%20admitted%20he%20may%20not%20always%20know%20which%20projects%20to%20choose.%20He%20will%20next%20be%20seen%20in%20'Farzi%20Season%202'.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A100%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22My%20father-in-law%20was%20given%20a%20year%20to%20live.%20We%20spent%20it%20traveling%20the%20world%20together.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223006%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Heather%2C%20her%20husband%2C%20and%20her%20father-in-law%20pose%20for%20a%20photo%20in%20a%20distillery.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a1f233cb4fb977f359836c0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222254%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20traveled%20the%20world%20with%20my%20father-in-law%20at%20the%20end%20of%20his%20life.%3Cp%3EHeather%20Storgaard%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EWhen%20my%20father-in-law%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flinkedin-connection-dating-marriage-cancer-treatment-2024-2%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Egiven%20a%20year%20to%20live%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20he%20told%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20that%20he%20wanted%20to%20travel.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt%20wasn't%20always%20easy%2C%20but%20together%2C%20we%20took%20six%20trips%20over%20nine%20months.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EOur%20travels%20created%20a%20bond%20that%20I%20still%20feel%20privileged%20to%20have%20experienced.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20February%202022%2C%20my%20father-in-law%2C%20Finn%2C%20was%20given%20a%20year%20to%20live.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20had%20peritoneal%20cancer%2C%20a%20rare%20type%20that%20affects%20the%20abdominal%20lining.%20Although%20it%20was%20everywhere%20and%20incurable%2C%20the%20doctors%20told%20us%20it%20likely%20wouldn't%20cause%20him%20significant%20pain%20until%20near%20the%20end.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20over%20a%20Scotch%2C%20I%20asked%20him%20what%20he%20wanted%20%E2%80%94%20if%20there%20were%20any%20people%20he%20wished%20to%20see%20or%20places%20he%20longed%20to%20visit.%20Somehow%2C%20I%20felt%20a%20strong%20need%20to%20fulfill%20his%20final%20wishes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETurns%20out%2C%20he%20wanted%20to%20travel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20Finn%20had%20retired%20to%20a%20farm%20in%20rural%20Denmark%2C%20he%20had%20always%20been%20the%20adventurous%20type%20%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoving-united-kingdom-to-los-angeles-differences-surprising-things-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emoving%20to%20California%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20early%20'70s%20despite%20not%20knowing%20anyone%20there%2C%20traveling%20through%20the%20Soviet%20Union%20in%20the%20'80s%2C%20and%20taking%20his%20family%20on%20vacation%20to%20Uganda%20and%20Kenya%20in%20the%202000s.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKnowing%20he%20only%20had%20a%20year%20left%20sparked%20a%20return%20to%20that%20thirst%20for%20new%20experiences%20of%20places%2C%20people%2C%20and%20cultures.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20first%2C%20the%20idea%20of%20traveling%20together%20felt%20almost%20daunting.%20Chemotherapy%20had%20already%20begun%20taking%20a%20toll%20on%20Finn%2C%20and%20we%20wanted%20to%20make%20sure%20he'd%20have%20access%20to%20reliable%20care%20if%20his%20health%20took%20a%20turn%20for%20the%20worse.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPlus%2C%20I%20knew%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20would%20both%20have%20to%20take%20a%20mix%20of%20paid%20and%20unpaid%20leave%20and%20use%20every%20holiday%20weekend%20we%20could%20in%20order%20to%20make%20it%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGiven%20the%20weight%20of%20Finn's%20diagnosis%2C%20however%2C%20we%20all%20felt%20a%20quiet%20intensity%20surrounding%20every%20decision%20and%20interaction.%20A%20few%20months%20later%2C%20we%20took%20a%20leap%20and%20embarked%20on%20our%20first%20big%20trip%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcountry-i-return-to-every-year-spain-frequent-traveler%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESeville%2C%20Spain%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222c7e0de9-0e66-4244-b7c9-e3ac7cbba8ce%5C%22%3EDuring%20our%20travels%2C%20I%20saw%20a%20different%20side%20to%20Finn%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Finn%20and%20his%20son%20sit%20on%20a%20tiled%20bench%20in%20Spain.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a1f2e842ab5f9757add82f4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFinn%20really%20enjoyed%20our%20trip%20to%20Seville.%3Cp%3EHeather%20Storgaard%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20we%20arrived%20in%20Spain%2C%20we%20spent%20time%20wandering%20the%20streets%2C%20marveling%20at%20the%20sand-colored%20buildings%2C%20decorative%20arches%2C%20and%20lush%20plant%20life%20in%20courtyards.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFinn%20was%20immediately%20struck%20by%20the%20smells%2C%20the%20vibrancy%20of%20the%20streets%2C%20and%20the%20sound%20of%20parakeets%20flying%20overhead.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERather%20than%20the%20somewhat%20apathetic%20attitude%20to%20life%20and%20social%20interactions%20we%20saw%20him%20adapt%20at%20home%2C%20he%20seemed%20different%20on%20this%20trip.%20He%20wanted%20to%20experience%20everything%20he%20could.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20he%20was%20far%20from%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmistakes-american-made-first-visit-japan-regrets-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eperfect%20visitor%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%20a%20sherry%20bar%2C%20where%20none%20of%20the%20staff%20spoke%20English%2C%20he%20decided%20he%20wanted%20a%20cup%20of%20tea.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20solution%20to%20the%20language%20barrier%20was%20song%20and%20dance%2C%20complete%20with%20a%20mime%20demonstrating%20a%20teapot.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20I%20was%20acutely%20embarrassed%2C%20but%20now%2C%20the%20memory%20is%20one%20I'll%20cherish%20forever.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20end%20of%20the%20trip%2C%20he%20wanted%20to%20know%20where%20we%20would%20head%20next.%20His%20ability%20to%20cope%20with%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feven-with-insurance-my-breast-cancer-treatment-was-expensive-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecancer%20treatment%3C%2Fa%3E%20seemed%20to%20hinge%20on%20having%20fixed%20plans%20to%20look%20forward%20to.%20However%2C%20I%20worried%20he%20needed%20more%20rest%20than%20he%20was%20allowing%20himself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22120ccb5d-93df-4c54-b563-001e2ae84846%5C%22%3EAs%20Finn's%20health%20declined%2C%20we%20learned%20to%20travel%20differently%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222363%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Finn%20poses%20for%20a%20photo%20while%20eating%20breakfast%20on%20an%20outdoor%20patio.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a1f2eae2ab5f9757add82f7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221772%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOver%20time%2C%20we%20traveled%20differently%20to%20accommodate%20Finn's%20declining%20energy%20levels.%3Cp%3EHeather%20Storgaard%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20fall%2C%20we%20took%20a%20trip%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fphotos-scottish-orkney-island-church-vacation-rental-renovation-2022-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EOrkney%20Islands%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20an%20archipelago%20off%20the%20coast%20of%20Scotland.%20By%20then%2C%20Finn's%20mobility%20and%20energy%20levels%20were%20noticeably%20lower%20than%20they%20had%20been%20in%20Spain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20even%20had%20to%20veto%20an%20extended%20tour%20of%20the%20St.%20Magnus%20Cathedral%2C%20a%20structure%20that%20my%20father-in-law%20had%20been%20deeply%20moved%20by.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20we%20adjusted%20to%20his%20energy%20levels%2C%20prioritizing%20slow%20breakfasts%20together%20and%20short%20walks%20that%20allowed%20Finn%20to%20feel%20connected%20to%20nature.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20skipped%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finside-luxury-ghost-whisky-distillery-revived-after-40-years-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etour%20of%20a%20whiskey%20distillery%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20managed%20to%20explore%20the%20magnificent%20sea%20cliffs%2C%20much%20to%20my%20surprise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222972%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Finn%20and%20his%20son%20stand%20near%20cliffs%20in%20the%20Orkney%20Islands.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a1f27c12ab5f9757add829c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222229%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFinn%20had%20enough%20energy%20to%20explore%20the%20cliffs%20in%20the%20Orkney%20Islands.%3Cp%3EHeather%20Storgaard%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOverall%2C%20we%20took%20six%20trips%20over%20nine%20months.%20Throughout%20our%20travels%2C%20friends%20reached%20out%20with%20well-intentioned%20concerns%20about%20us%20exploring%20the%20world%20with%20him.%20But%2C%20in%20some%20ways%2C%20it%20felt%20like%20we%20were%20only%20just%20hitting%20our%20stride.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20we%20couldn't%20ignore%20the%20gravity%20of%20the%20situation%2C%20and%20the%20doctor's%20predicted%20time%20scale%20proved%20spot-on.%20We%20took%20our%20final%20trip%20together%20to%20Scotland%20at%20the%20end%20of%202022%2C%20where%20Finn%20blamed%20his%20lethargy%20and%20nausea%20on%20food%20and%20drink.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20it%20was%20becoming%20clear%20to%20me%20that%20this%20was%20the%20end%20of%20our%20travels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ae4a2c9d-ac20-41ae-9237-3aabf58ec730%5C%22%3EI'll%20always%20be%20grateful%20for%20the%20experiences%20we%20shared%20during%20his%20final%20year%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20from%20his%20hospital%20bed%2C%20he%20told%20relatives%20and%20friends%20all%20about%20our%20adventures%2C%20recommending%20the%20best%20views%20in%20Orkney%20and%20must-visit%20restaurants%20in%20Poland.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20few%20months%20after%20our%20last%20trip%2C%20Finn%20passed%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20his%20funeral%2C%20people%20I%20hardly%20knew%20told%20me%20how%20inspired%20they%20were%20by%20his%20enduring%20thirst%20for%20life%20and%20new%20experiences.%20And%20to%20be%20honest%2C%20I%20was%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20father-in-law%20taught%20me%20how%20to%20work%20through%20challenges%20and%20find%20positivity%20even%20in%20the%20toughest%20of%20times.%20Rather%20than%20waiting%20for%20that%20momentous%20occasion%20%E2%80%94%20a%20big%20birthday%20or%20anniversary%20%E2%80%94%20I%20learned%20that%20spontaneous%20and%20imperfect%20experiences%20can%20be%20even%20more%20meaningful.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPlus%2C%20our%20travels%20together%20created%20a%20bond%20among%20my%20husband%2C%20his%20dad%2C%20and%20me%20that%20I%20still%20feel%20privileged%20to%20have%20experienced.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftraveled-with-family-member-end-of-life-terminally-ill-benefits-2026-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1781175781000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a1f233cb4fb977f359836c0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bu