ast%20and%20en%20masse.%3Cp%3EDiego%20Herrera%20Carcedo%2FAnadolu%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20war%20in%20Ukraine%20is%20showing%20NATO%20it%20needs%20weapons%20available%20now%2C%20even%20if%20they're%20imperfect.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EOfficials%20say%20good-enough%20gear%20matters%20more%20than%20perfect%20systems%20that%20arrive%20too%20late.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20German%20Army's%20vice%20chief%20wants%20%26quot%3Busable%20capabilities%20today%2C%26quot%3B%20not%20the%20%26quot%3Bperfect%20solution%20in%2010%20years.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ERIGA%2C%20Latvia%20%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-did-russia-invade-ukraine-putin-politics-motive-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ERussia's%20invasion%20of%20Ukraine%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20shown%20NATO%20that%20it%20can't%20afford%20to%20wait%2010%20years%20for%20perfect%20weapons.%20It%20needs%20weapons%20that%20are%20good%20enough%20and%20available%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFears%20of%20further%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-better-positioned-attack-europe-before-ukraine-war-nato-lithuania-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ERussian%20aggression%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20pushed%20the%20West%20to%20absorb%20a%20host%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-sharing-weapons-and-battle-expertise-with-west-tables-turned-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elessons%20from%20Ukraine's%20fight%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20Western%20officials%20have%20been%20warning%20that%20arsenals%20are%20insufficient.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHeico%20H%C3%BCbner%2C%20the%20vice%20chief%20of%20the%20German%20Army%2C%20said%20his%20country%20is%20%26quot%3Bpursuing%20a%20very%20pragmatic%20approach%26quot%3B%20focused%20not%20on%20having%20the%20%26quot%3Bperfect%20solution%20in%2010%20years%2C%20but%20usable%20capabilities%20today.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20time%20is%20%26quot%3Ba%20decisive%20factor%20of%20military%20credibility.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUkraine%20has%20demonstrated%20how%20rapidly%20innovation%20cycles%20evolve%20today%2C%20and%20adaptation%20no%20longer%20happens%20over%20years%20as%20in%20the%20past.%20Today%2C%20in%20many%20cases%2C%20it%20happens%20within%20weeks%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20at%20a%20drone%20summit%20in%20Latvia%2C%20he%20said%20the%20war%20has%20shown%20that%20the%20real%20test%20is%20no%20longer%20who%20can%20design%20the%20most%20advanced%20technology%2C%20but%20who%20can%20produce%20it%20at%20scale%20and%20get%20it%20into%20troops'%20hands%20fast%20enough%20to%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECarsten%20Breuer%2C%20Germany's%20chief%20of%20defense%2C%20made%20a%20similar%20point%20at%20the%20summit%2C%20saying%20the%20first%20question%20in%20weapons%20procurement%20is%20whether%20a%20system%20is%20%26quot%3Bavailable%20in%20time%26quot%3B%20because%20Germany%20believes%20Russia%20could%20be%20ready%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnato-would-face-heavier-losses-than-ukraine-russia-war-officer-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eattack%20NATO%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%202029%2C%20meaning%20%26quot%3Bwe%20have%20to%20be%20ready%20as%20soon%20as%20possible.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20better%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bto%20buy%20off%20the%20shelves%20than%20to%20procure%20something%20which%20has%20to%20be%20developed%20and%20will%20be%20here%20in%202035.%26quot%3B%20Breuer%20added%20that%20allies%20need%20%26quot%3Bthe%20advantage%20of%20speed%20because%20this%20urgency%20counts.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20alarm%20bells%20have%20been%20sounding%20across%20the%20alliance%2C%20but%20they%20are%20taking%20on%20new%20urgency.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGen.%20James%20E.%20Rainey%2C%20then%20the%20commanding%20general%20of%20US%20Army%20Futures%20Command%2C%20wrote%20in%202024%20that%20%26quot%3Bperfect%20is%20the%20enemy%20of%20good%20enough%2C%26quot%3B%20arguing%20that%2C%20in%20many%20cases%2C%20the%20US%20was%20%26quot%3Ballowing%20the%20aspirational%20to%20stand%20in%20the%20way%20of%20the%20doable.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20technologies%20that%20would%20be%20useful%20in%20our%20formations%20right%20now%20but%20are%20not%20yet%20fielded%20because%20we%20are%20waiting%20until%20they%20can%20do%20even%20more%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETarja%20Jaakkola%2C%20NATO's%20assistant%20secretary%20general%20for%20defense%20industry%2C%20innovation%2C%20and%20armaments%2C%20shared%20at%20the%20drone%20summit%20in%20Latvia%20that%20the%20alliance%20is%20looking%20at%20what%20capabilities%20civilian%20and%20dual-use%20companies%20can%20give%20%26quot%3Bfaster%2C%20at%20scale%2C%20but%20also%20cheaper.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECivilian%20technology%20is%20typically%20cheaper%20and%20already%20available.%20%26quot%3BSo%20we%20are%20very%20much%20talking%20about%20what%20is%20good%20enough.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f740361b-6b6d-4ab9-bebf-6da31ee31b3d%5C%22%3EUkraine's%20different%20approach%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENATO%20Secretary%20General%20Mark%20Rutte%20said%20last%20year%20that%20the%20alliance%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fadvantage-cheap-weapons-modern-war-not-just-their-price-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emakes%20weapons%3C%2Fa%3E%20too%20slowly%2C%20and%20should%20make%20less%20effective%20ones%20so%20it%20could%20work%20faster%3A%20%26quot%3BSpeed%20is%20of%20the%20essence%2C%20not%20perfection.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20Ukraine%20makes%2C%20approves%2C%20and%20uses%20equipment%20that%20could%20be%20rated%20a%20%26quot%3B6%20to%207%26quot%3B%20out%20of%2010%2C%20while%20NATO%20militaries%20insist%20on%20reaching%20%26quot%3B9%20or%2010.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDefense%20companies%2C%20both%20in%20and%20out%20of%20Ukraine%2C%20are%20taking%20note.%20Kristian%20Brost%2C%20the%20general%20manager%20for%20the%20US%20division%20of%20Robin%20Radar%2C%20a%20Dutch%20company%20that%20makes%20drone-detection%20radar%20systems%20used%20by%20Ukraine%20and%20US%20allies%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20war%20shows%20an%20imperfect%20answer%20%26quot%3Bright%20now%2C%20sometimes%2C%20is%20better%20than%20a%20perfect%20solution%20later.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20there%20is%20%26quot%3Ba%20lot%20we%20can%20learn%26quot%3B%20from%20Ukraine%2C%20which%20is%20%26quot%3Bin%20a%20spot%20where%20sometimes%20they%20need%20duct%20tape%20and%20rubber%20bands.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUltimately%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20that's%20in%20itself%20a%20lesson%3A%20Use%20what%20works%2C%20use%20what%20is%20cheap.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223d786019-32fd-41bf-9f1f-45b6517300e8%5C%22%3EBuilding%20faster%20and%20cheaper%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ERussia's%20war%20has%20shown%20the%20West%20that%20Moscow%20is%20willing%20to%20use%20attritional%20tactics%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-invasion-west-focused-too-much-weapon-quantity-over-numbers-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Echew%20through%20masses%20of%20weaponry%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20kind%20of%20war%20the%20West%20hasn't%20faced%20in%20decades%20but%20could%20in%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAttritional%20warfare%20is%20grinding%20combat%20that%20consumes%20huge%20numbers%20of%20troops%2C%20weapons%2C%20and%20ammunition%20over%20time.%20It%20has%20led%20to%20a%20new%20way%20of%20thinking%20about%20weaponry%20in%20the%20West%2C%20which%2C%20since%20the%20Cold%20War%2C%20has%20focused%20on%20having%20fewer%20pieces%20of%20advanced%20equipment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20much%20of%20the%20West%20sees%20larger%20volumes%20of%20cheaper%20weapons%20that%20it%20can%20get%20quickly%20as%20essential%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESir%20John%20Stringer%2C%20NATO's%20Deputy%20Supreme%20Allied%20Commander%20for%20Europe%2C%20said%20at%20the%20recent%20drone%20summit%20that%20the%20West%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-shows-need-make-weapons-quickly-even-imperfect-nato-rutte-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eneeds%20to%20move%20much%20faster%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20get%20%26quot%3Bcomfortable%20with%20procurement%20cycles%20which%20are%20faster%20than%20what%20we%20have%20been%20brought%20up%20with%2C%26quot%3B%20instead%20of%20big%20programs%20that%20last%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20West%20is%20now%20%26quot%3Bin%20a%20race%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20and%20%26quot%3Bwe%20need%20to%20be%20in%20that%20space%20where%20we%20are%20testing%2C%20adjusting%2C%20failing%20and%20learning%2C%20procuring%20much%2C%20much%20faster%20than%20has%20been%20the%20case.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20means%20%26quot%3Bthe%20what%2C%20how%2C%20where%2C%20and%20when%20of%20production%20is%20going%20to%20change.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-shows-nato-perfect-weapons-10-years-maybe-late-speed-2026-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1781171641000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a28566f67142ea6832ce909%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-shows-nato-perfect-weapons-10-years-maybe-late-speed-2026-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ukraine%20is%20showing%20allies%20that%20it%20needs%20large%20masses%20of%20weaponry%20that%20are%20available%20fast%2C%20and%20it%20can't%20afford%20to%20wait%20only%20for%20perfect%20weapons.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22sbaker%40insider.com%20(Sin%C3%A9ad%20Baker)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20World%20Cup%20guide%20for%20people%20who%20don't%20care%20about%20soccer%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223086%5C%22%20alt%3D