20of%20the%20%26quot%3BTartan%20Army.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3ELucy%20Lu%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ERory%20Phillips-Hunter%20was%20in%20tears%20when%20he%20watched%20Scotland%20beat%20Denmark%20at%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finside-the-cost-of-attending-the-2026-fifa-world-cup-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EFIFA%20World%20Cup%3C%2Fa%3E%20qualifiers%20in%20November.%20For%20the%20first%20time%20since%201998%2C%20his%20national%20team%20had%20qualified%20for%20the%20biggest%20event%20in%20sports.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20turned%20to%20my%20fianc%C3%A9e%20at%20the%20time%2C%20as%20soon%20as%20the%20full-time%20whistle%20went%2C%20and%20I%20said%3A%20'We're%20going.%20I%20don't%20care%20what%20it%20takes.%20We're%20getting%20across%20to%20America%2C'%26quot%3B%20he%20recounted%20to%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20was%20until%20he%20realized%20the%20Scottish%20national%20team's%20matches%20would%20be%20played%20at%20Gillette%20Stadium%20in%20Foxborough%2C%20Massachusetts%2C%20and%20that%20hotel%20prices%20in%20nearby%20Boston%20were%20far%20beyond%20what%20he%20could%20afford.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20eight-day%20stay%20in%20the%20US%20for%20two%20people%20would%20cost%20%248%2C000%20total%2C%2037-year-old%20Phillips-Hunter%20estimated.%20He%20was%20born%20in%20Hawick%2C%20a%20town%20in%20the%20Scottish%20Borders%2C%20and%20now%20works%20as%20an%20estate%20and%20maintenance%20manager%20at%20a%20farm%20in%20North%20West%20England%2C%20earning%20about%20%C2%A333%2C000%20(%2444%2C000)%20a%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224579%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Rory%20Phillips-Hunter%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a29b9ac59f798e5451f6379%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225724%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERory%20Phillips-Hunter%20is%20pictured%20here%20wearing%20a%20Glengarry%20bonnet%2C%20a%20traditional%20Scottish%20cap.%3Cp%3ECraig%20Mcintosh%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20looked%20at%20the%20map%20to%20see%20what%20else%20was%20close%20to%20Gillette%20Stadium%2C%20and%20stumbled%20across%20Providence%2C%20Rhode%20Island%2C%20about%20a%2040-minute%20drive%20from%20the%20stadium.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20when%20it%20all%20started%20to%20come%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPhillips-Hunter%20is%20one%20of%20an%20estimated%207%2C000%20Scottish%20national%20soccer%20fans%2C%20collectively%20known%20as%20the%20Tartan%20Army%2C%20planning%20to%20come%20to%20Providence%20for%20the%20World%20Cup%20in%20time%20for%20Scotland's%20first%20game%20this%20weekend.%20Like%20many%20of%20them%2C%20it%20will%20be%20Phillips-Hunter's%20first%20time%20attending%20a%20World%20Cup.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20fans%20have%20been%20working%20with%20local%20government%20departments%20and%20businesses%20to%20arrange%20cheaper%20accommodation%2C%20group%20transport%2C%20and%20big%20events%20to%20celebrate%20Scotland's%20return%20to%20the%20World%20Cup.%20Their%20plans%20have%20ballooned%20into%20a%20citywide%20embrace%20of%20the%20Tartan%20Army%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Espearheaded%20by%20eight%20organizers%2C%20including%20Phillips-Hunter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20some%2C%20the%20descent%20upon%20the%20midsize%2C%20coastal%20American%20city%20of%20195%2C000%20people%20(1.7%20million%20if%20you%20include%20the%20broader%20metro%20area)%20is%20a%20way%20to%20keep%20costs%20down.%20This%20year's%20event%20is%20shaping%20up%20to%20be%2C%20by%20far%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffifa-world-cup-ticket-price-travel-cost-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20most%20expensive%20World%20Cup%20on%20record%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Fans%20from%20around%20the%20world%20have%20been%20taking%20measures%20such%20as%20carpooling%2C%20sharing%20Airbnbs%2C%20or%20opting%20for%20less%20popular%20games%20to%20be%20able%20to%20attend.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20others%2C%20it's%20about%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20for%20the%20small%20businesses%20set%20to%20receive%20the%206%2C000-strong%20team%20of%20Scotland%20supporters%2C%20it's%20looking%20like%20one%20heck%20of%20a%20payday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225456%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Scottish%20flag%20outside%20a%20bar%20in%20Providence%2C%20RI%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a296884a74097c573988ba4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223637%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20Scottish%20flag%20hangs%20in%20front%20of%20a%20bar%20ahead%20of%20the%20FIFA%20World%20Cup%20in%20Providence.%3Cp%3ELucy%20Lu%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c243d5f6-7013-466b-bdd7-b8e78aae5fbc%5C%22%3E'Look%2C%20there's%20going%20to%20be%20a%20few%20people%20coming'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20late%20December%2C%20Phillips-Hunter%20joined%20a%20WhatsApp%20group%20with%20other%20Scotland%20fans%20who%20planned%20to%20travel%20to%20Providence%20for%20the%20World%20Cup.%20There%20were%20about%2025%20people%20in%20it%20at%20the%20time%2C%20and%20the%20group%20had%20been%20shared%20on%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDavie%20Hood%2C%20a%2060-year-old%20civil%20servant%20from%20Glasgow%2C%20was%20one%20of%20these%20early%20members%20and%20organizers.%20He%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20WhatsApp%20group%20grew%20to%20400%20members%20in%20January%20and%20has%20swelled%20to%20over%201%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Providence%20Tartan%20Army%20quickly%20gained%20traction%20in%20Scottish%20media%3B%20their%20Facebook%20group%20has%20over%2013%2C000%20followers.%20Providence's%20Department%20of%20Art%2C%20Culture%2C%20and%20Tourism%2C%20as%20well%20as%20organizers%2C%20expect%20between%206%2C000%20and%207%2C000%20members%20of%20the%20Tartan%20Army%20to%20be%20in%20Providence%20for%20the%20World%20Cup.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225359%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jim%20Brown%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a296e5ab19390180e4cf09a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223644%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJim%20Brown%20wears%20a%20Tartan%20Army%20shirt%20at%20Trinity%20Brewhouse%20in%20Providence.%3Cp%3ELucy%20Lu%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20organizers'%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Efirst%20tasks%20was%20to%20find%20affordable%20transport%20to%20the%20game%2C%20which%20they%20said%20didn't%20exist%20earlier%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETheir%20solution%20was%20to%20hire%20American%20school%20buses%20to%20cut%20costs.%20They%20plan%20to%20use%2021%20buses%20to%20transport%201%2C100%20supporters%20to%20and%20from%20the%20Scotland%20v.%20Haiti%20game%20this%20weekend%20and%2020%20buses%20to%20transport%201%2C050%20supporters%20to%20and%20from%20the%20Scotland%20v.%20Morocco%20game%20on%20June%2019.%20Both%20matches%20take%20place%20at%20Gillette%20Stadium.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20about%20%2450%20each%2C%20supporters%20get%20a%20round-trip%20bus%20ticket%2C%20a%20small%20donation%20toward%20a%20local%20charity%2C%20and%20beers%2C%20cider%2C%20wine%2C%20and%20soft%20drinks%20for%20the%20trip.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20then%2C%20the%20Boston%20Host%20Committee%2C%20which%20represents%20FIFA%2C%20has%20also%20launched%20a%20%2495%20round-trip%20bus%20service%20from%20Providence%20to%20the%20stadium.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENext%20up%20was%20accommodation.%20The%20organizers%20wrote%20to%20a%20series%20of%20hotels%20in%20Providence%20to%20secure%20deals.%20Some%20Tartan%20Army%20fans%20are%20staying%20at%20the%20Providence%20Marriott%20Downtown%2C%20organizers%20said.%20The%20hotel%20offered%20them%20lower%20room%20rates%2C%20plus%20a%20%2420%20food-and-beverage%20voucher%20to%20use%20at%20the%20hotel.%20For%20a%20king-size%20room%2C%20Phillips-Hunter%20is%20spending%20%24288%20a%20night%20for%20two%20people.%20These%20rooms%20are%20currently%20listed%20for%20over%20%24400%20a%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Marriott%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225396%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20World%20Cup%20sign%20in%20Providence%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a29694159f798e5451f58e2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223597%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20FIFA%20World%20Cup%20Fan%20Zone%20at%20Station%20Park%20in%20Providence.%3Cp%3ELucy%20Lu%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Tartan%20Army%20organizers%20also%20reached%20out%20to%20Providence's%20Department%20of%20Art%2C%20Culture%2C%20and%20Tourism%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-things-to-do-providence-rhode-island-according-to-local-2021-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EProvidence%20Tourism%20Council%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Efor%20information%20on%20finding%20affordable%20accommodation%20and%20permission%20to%20host%20larger%20events%20in%20the%20city.%20%26quot%3BLook%2C%20there's%20going%20to%20be%20a%20few%20people%20coming%2C%26quot%3B%20Hood%20recalled%20telling%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJoe%20Wilson%2C%20director%20of%20this%20department%2C%20said%20his%20team%20has%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ebeen%20helping%20to%20find%20housing%20and%20arrange%20buses%20from%20the%20fan%20zone.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThey're%20also%20helping%20facilitate%20a%20bagpipe-and-kilt%20procession%20downtown.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20tell%20you%2C%20we've%20been%20so%20busy%2C%26quot%3B%20Wilson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2254980477-fbce-4148-9036-a8cebd814581%5C%22%3EPints%20at%20the%20ready%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELocal%20businesses%20are%20preparing%20for%20the%20Tartan%20Army%20windfall.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20average%20spend%20is%20going%20to%20be%20about%20%242%2C000%20per%20person%2C%20with%20accommodation%2C%20food%2C%20rent%2C%20and%20tourist%20attractions%2C%26quot%3B%20Hood%20estimated.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20lot%20of%20money%20going%20into%20their%20economy%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225581%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tartan%20Army%20sign%20at%20a%20bar%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a29698659f798e5451f58e5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223721%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20neon%20%26quot%3BTartan%20Army%26quot%3B%20sign%20at%20Providence%20G%20Pub.%3Cp%3ELucy%20Lu%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWilson%20said%20the%20economic%20impact%20will%20be%20felt%20strongly.%20The%20entire%20state%20of%20Rhode%20Island%20is%20expecting%20as%20many%20as%202.2%20million%20visitors%20total%20from%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fworld-cup-is-springboard-moment-us-soccer-ceo-says-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EWorld%20Cup%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAny%20amount%20of%20%5Bfoot%5D%20traffic%E2%80%A6%20will%20be%20a%20benefit%20for%20our%20city%2C%26quot%3B%20Wilson%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Esaid.%20%26quot%3BIf%20we%20have%20an%20extra%2050%2C000%20people%2C%20that%20is%20a%20big%20impact%20for%20us.%20I'm%20excited%20for%20our%20small%20businesses%2C%20for%20our%20residents.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20June%2018%2C%20the%20Providence%20Tartan%20Army%20is%20scheduled%20to%20hold%20a%20fan%20march%20accompanied%20by%20bagpipe%20players.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20march%20ends%20at%20a%20local%20park%2C%20where%20a%205%2C000-person%20event%20called%20%26quot%3BTA%20in%20the%20Park%26quot%3B%20is%20expected.%20It's%20a%20collaboration%20with%20local%20brewing%20cooperative%20The%20Guild%20Brewing%20Company%2C%20among%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225369%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jeremy%20Duffy%20and%20Devin%20Kelly%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a2969c059f798e5451f58e6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223622%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJeremy%20Duffy%20(L)%20and%20Devin%20Kelly%20(R)%2C%20cofounders%20of%20Guild%20Brewing%20Company%2C%20hold%20a%20banner%20in%20support%20of%20the%20Scottish%20National%20Football%20Team.%3Cp%3ELucy%20Lu%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Guild%20Brewing%20Company%20cofounder%2C%20Jeremy%20Duffy%2C%20said%20they%20plan%20to%20bring%20more%20than%20700%20cases%20%E2%80%94%2016%2C000%20pints%20%E2%80%94%20of%20beer%20to%20the%20event.%20There%20will%20be%205%2C000%20personalized%20beer%20cans%20for%20the%20Tartan%20Army.%20He%20wouldn't%20comment%20on%20how%20much%20he%20will%20make%20from%20beer%20sales%2C%20but%20said%20his%20plan%20is%20to%20cover%20the%20costs%20of%20putting%20it%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20the%20plan%20is%20to%20head%20to%20one%20of%20the%20city's%20popular%20spots%20for%20sports%20fans%2C%20Providence%20G%20Pub%2C%20for%20an%20after-party.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIvan%20Kristicevic%2C%20hospitality%20and%20community%20manager%20for%20G%20Hospitality%2C%20which%20owns%20the%20pub%2C%20said%20it%20plans%20to%20become%20the%20Tartan%20Army's%20unofficial%20HQ.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKristicevic%20wouldn't%20disclose%20how%20much%20he%20expects%20to%20make%20from%20the%20events%2C%20but%20said%20they%20are%20doing%20a%20%26quot%3Bvery%2C%20very%20large%20preorder%26quot%3B%20of%20food%20and%20drinks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225535%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ivan%20Kristicevic%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a296a53a74097c573988bbc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223690%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIvan%20Kristicevic%2C%20manager%20of%20the%20Providence%20G%20Pub%2C%20poses%20for%20a%20portrait%20at%20the%20bar%20ahead%20of%20welcoming%20the%20Tartan%20Army.%3Cp%3ELucy%20Lu%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20the%20spirit%20of%20traveling%20with%20the%20Tartan%20Army%20isn't%20just%20about%20keeping%20costs%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGareth%20Greenshields%2C%20a%2043-year-old%20Scottish%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eclinical%20operations%20manager%2C%20said%20he%20first%20came%20across%20the%20group%20on%20WhatsApp%20groups%20and%20quickly%20decided%20that%20was%20where%20he%20wanted%20to%20stay%20when%20watching%20the%20Scotland%20games.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI've%20managed%20to%20create%20a%20network.%20I've%20got%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20that%20I'm%20going%20to%20be%20pairing%20up%20with%20when%20I'm%20over%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20Greenshields%2C%20who%20is%20based%20in%20Switzerland%2C%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe've%20had%20flags%20made.%20I'm%20going%20to%20be%20piping%20over%20there%2C%20so%20I'm%20in%20touch%20with%20a%20few%20of%20the%20bagpipers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20me%2C%20it%20was%20all%20about%20the%20camaraderie%20rather%20than%20cost.%20And%20that's%20a%20good%20privilege%20to%20have%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22634785e2-ad57-4d20-af62-a2468686cd92%5C%22%3E'Making%20memories%20that%20will%20quite%20literally%20last%20a%20lifetime'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EA%20key%20Tartan%20Army%20tradition%20when%20traveling%20for%20a%20game%20is%20to%20leave%20a%20donation%20to%20a%20local%20children's%20charity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20do%20so%2C%20they%20are%20selling%20merchandise%20to%20fans%2C%20such%20as%20%C2%A33%20(%244)%20badges%20and%20%C2%A320%20(%2427)%20T-shirts%2C%20with%20all%20proceeds%20going%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fray-dalio-christmas-gifts-charity-gift-cards-holiday-season-shopping-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eto%20charity%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20badges%20are%20emblazoned%20with%20the%20Scottish%20Football%20Association%20crest%20and%20the%20phrase%20%26quot%3BI've%20met%20the%20Providence%20Tartan%20Army%26quot%3B%3B%20the%20T-shirts%20feature%20the%20Scottish%20and%20American%20flags.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225126%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tartan%20Army%20decorations%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a296aa659f798e5451f58f1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223573%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EKristicevic%20ordered%20decorations%20for%20his%20pub%20ahead%20of%20welcoming%20the%20Tartan%20Army.%3Cp%3ELucy%20Lu%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20far%2C%20they%20have%20raised%20%2410%2C000%20for%20the%20local%20Hasbro%20Children's%20Hospital%2C%20%2410%2C000%20for%20Project%20Goal%20%E2%80%94%20a%20grassroots%20football%20organization%20in%20the%20city%20%E2%80%94%20and%20%246%2C500%20for%20the%20Rhode%20Island%20Highlanders%20pipe%20band.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPhillips-Hunter%20said%20he%20gets%20emotional%20when%20he%20thinks%20about%20the%20fundraising%20effort%20and%20all%20the%20organizing%20that%20went%20into%20getting%20Scotland%20fans%20to%20Providence%20at%20a%20price%20they%20could%20afford.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20without%20the%20school%20buses%20and%20Marriott%20hotel%20deal%2C%20it%20would%20have%20been%20difficult%20for%20him%20to%20go.%20He%20had%20already%20sold%20his%20pickup%20truck%20to%20get%20a%20cheaper-running%20car%20and%20had%20maxed%20out%20a%20credit%20card%20to%20afford%20the%20trip.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe's%20spending%20just%20under%20%246%2C000%20total%20on%20the%20trip.%20This%20includes%20travel%20and%20accommodation%20for%20himself%20and%20his%20fianc%C3%A9e%2C%20and%20the%20%24600%20he's%20budgeted%20for%20spending%20money%20while%20he's%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20would've%20found%20a%20way%20to%20have%20gone%2C%20but%20it%20would%20have%20left%20me%20in%20financial%20peril%20far%20more%20so%20than%20I%20already%20am%2C%20had%20the%20deals%20not%20already%20been%20available%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20sit%20back%20now%2C%20and%20I%20think%2C%20'right%E2%80%A6I'm%20going%20to%20be%20on%20a%20plane%2C%20going%20across%20to%20America%2C%20from%20a%20little%20boy%20of%20nine%20years%20old%2C%20watching%20Scotland%20the%20last%20time%20we%20were%20in%20a%20World%20Cup%2C%20to%20knowing%20that%20I'll%20be%20partly%20responsible%20for%20upward%20of%2010%2C000%20peopl