ss%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221913%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Store%20employee%20picks%20an%20order%20from%20candy%20and%20snack%20shelves%20in%20a%20brightly%20lit%20grocery%20aisle.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a29e5ececc428964ed26de7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221435%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EDominick%20Reuter%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EWalmart's%20head%20of%20growth%20says%20AI%20commerce%20presents%20an%20opportunity%20for%20a%20more%20strategic%20approach%20to%20ads.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAds%20have%20already%20overrun%20many%20conventional%20search%20engines%2C%20and%20they're%20coming%20to%20some%20AI%20platforms.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EFor%20now%2C%20the%20company%20said%20it's%20benefiting%20most%20from%20learning%20how%20people%20interact%20with%20chatbots.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ERetailers%20like%20Walmart%20are%20wading%20into%20AI-powered%20shopping%2C%20and%20their%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-super-bowl-openai-chatgpt-ads-claude-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eads%20are%20coming%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWalmart's%20chief%20growth%20officer%2C%20Seth%20Dallaire%2C%20said%20this%20new%20tech%20calls%20for%20a%20more%20strategic%20approach%20to%20advertising%20that%20can%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-ai-shopping-changing-online-retail-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eimprove%20the%20shopping%20experience%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20retail%20giant%20has%20been%20testing%20ads%20in%20its%20AI-powered%20shopping%20assistant%2C%20Sparky%2C%20since%20last%20fall%2C%20but%20the%20company%20has%20said%20the%20presence%20of%20sponsored%20listings%20in%20the%20chat%20is%20significantly%20lower%20than%20what%20customers%20see%20in%20conventional%20search%20results.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe'll%20be%20careful%20to%20watch%20our%20customers%20and%20how%20they're%20using%20these%20tools%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20Wednesday%20during%20the%20Evercore%20ISI%20Consumer%20and%20Retail%20conference.%20%26quot%3BAdvertising%20and%20retail%20media%20will%20have%20a%20role%20to%20play%20because%20it%20helps%20customers%20shop.%20It's%20not%20an%20interruptive%20experience%2C%20it's%20contextually%20relevant.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDallaire%20oversees%20Walmart's%20ads%20business%2C%20which%20has%20become%20a%20significant%20revenue%20stream%20in%20its%20own%20right%20over%20the%20last%20few%20years.%20Its%20revenue%20grew%2046%25%20last%20year%20to%20%246.4%20billion.%20Its%20latest%20moves%20are%20setting%20the%20company%20up%20to%20capture%20a%20slice%20of%20the%20growing%20pie%20of%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcontent-na1.emarketer.com%2Fus-ai-advertising-forecast-2026%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20AI%20advertising%20dollars%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20Dallaire%20is%20in%20charge%20of%20growing%20Walmart's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhigh-income-shoppers-boost-walmarts-e-commerce-business-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ee-commerce%20marketplace%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Walmart%20Plus%20membership%20program%2C%20and%20said%20ads%20also%20have%20to%20improve%20merchandise%20sales%20and%20member%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20ads%20overwhelm%20a%20customer%20and%20cause%20them%20to%20abandon%20their%20cart%20without%20making%20a%20purchase%2C%20that%20doesn't%20work%20for%20Dallaire.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20advertising%20can%20help%20introduce%20shoppers%20to%20new%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20like%20to%20be%20exposed%20to%20new%20products%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BAdvertising%20plays%20a%20critical%20role%20in%20that.%20In%20fact%2C%20it's%20very%20similar%20to%20merchandising.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20now%2C%20Dallaire%C2%A0said%C2%A0Walmart%20is%20benefiting%20more%20from%20learning%20how%20people%20interact%20with%20its%20Sparky%20shopping%20assistant%20than%20it%20is%20from%20the%20ads%20it%20has%20included%20in%20the%20chatbot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20types%20of%20prompts%20that%20we%20get%20from%20customers%20in%20those%20agentic%20environments%20are%20quite%20different%20than%20what%20maybe%20historically%20we've%20seen%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20a%20customer%20might%20tell%20Sparky%20they're%20concerned%20about%20allergies%20and%20are%20looking%20for%20a%20laundry%20detergent%20that%20could%20help.%20Previously%2C%20they%20would%20have%20simply%20asked%20for%20fragrance-free%20detergent.%20With%20these%20longer%20conversations%2C%20Walmart%20doesn't%20have%20to%20make%20as%20many%20guesses%20about%20what%20shoppers%20want%20and%20risk%20serving%20up%20an%20irrelevant%20ad.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20that's%20how%20our%20customers%20are%20coming%20to%20us%20to%20shop%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bwe%20need%20to%20orient%20ourselves%20around%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwalmart-growth-chief-says-ai-is-rewriting-ad-strategy-2026-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1781171282000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a29e5ececc428964ed26de7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwalmart-growth-chief-says-ai-is-rewriting-ad-strategy-2026-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ads%20have%20already%20overrun%20conventional%20search%20results%2C%20but%20Walmart's%20head%20of%20growth%20is%20taking%20a%20slower%2C%20more%20strategic%20approach%20to%20ads%20in%20AI%20commerce.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22dreuter%40businessinsider.com%20(Dominick%20Reuter)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Napoleon%20CLARIFIES%20on%20MISSING%20