by%20Deol%20credits%20his%20wife%2C%20Tanya%2C%20as%20his%20backbone%20and%20inspiration%2C%20especially%20during%20his%20career%20slump%20and%20struggles%20with%20alcohol.%20She%20financially%20supported%20the%20family%20and%20raised%20their%20sons%20while%20he%20was%20in%20a%20difficult%20phase%20for%20over%20a%20decade.%20Deol%20also%20acknowledges%20his%20mother's%20quiet%20strength%20and%20the%20often-unrecognized%20contributions%20of%20women%20in%20households.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20Army%20soldiers%20say%20you%20can't%20just%20pour%20AI%20on%20new%20warfighting%20tech%20like%20ranch%20dressing%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226720%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Soldiers%20wearing%20camouflage%20walk%20along%20a%20dry%20field%20with%20a%20cloudy%20blue%20sky%20in%20the%20background.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a299653b19390180e4cf980%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224480%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELast%20month%2C%20soldiers%20conducted%20a%20live-fire%20exercise%20in%20Colorado%2C%20marking%20the%20latest%20test%20of%20NGC2.%3Cp%3EUS%20Army%20photo%20by%20Staff%20Sgt.%20Richard%20Stewart%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ESoldiers%20working%20on%20the%20US%20Army's%20NGC2%20platform%20said%20the%20use%20of%20AI%20was%20deliberate%20with%20guardrails.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAI%20helped%20troops%20analyze%20data%20for%20targeting%20purposes%2C%20as%20well%20as%20predicting%20ammunition%20and%20supplies.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ENGC2%20is%20the%20Army's%20new%20warfighting%20platform%20that's%20been%20developed%20over%20a%20series%20of%20tests.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20US%20Army%20tests%20its%20new%20warfighting%20software%2C%20soldiers%20say%20they%20are%20trying%20to%20use%20artificial%20intelligence%20for%20specific%20battlefield%20problems%2C%20not%20treat%20it%20as%20a%20fix%20for%20everything.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESoldiers%20said%20that%20their%20approach%20to%20putting%20AI%20capabilities%20into%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Farmy-on-move-future-war-hiding-command-posts-in-spectrum-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ENext%20Generation%20Command%20and%20Control%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20or%20NGC2%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ethe%20Army's%20new%20battlefield%20software%20platform%2C%20is%20perhaps%20best%20described%20by%20ranch%20dressing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20folks%20approach%20AI%20the%20same%20way%20they%20deal%20with%20ranch%20dressing%2C%26quot%3B%20Maj.%20Dave%20Hickox%2C%20the%20collection%20manager%20for%20the%20Army's%204th%20Infantry%20Division%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BThey%20don't%20know%20what's%20in%20it%20or%20how%20it's%20made%2C%20but%20they%20think%20that%20if%20you%20sprinkle%20it%20on%20anything%2C%20it%20makes%20it%20better.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20his%20division%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bwe're%20taking%20a%20more%20intentional%20and%20methodical%20approach%20to%20understanding%20the%20AI%20we're%20using%20as%20well%20as%20how%20and%20where%20to%20incorporate%20it%20to%20ensure%20it%20is%20enhancing%20our%20ability%20to%20identify%20and%20prosecute%20targets.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEssentially%2C%20each%20use%20of%20AI%20has%20to%20earn%20its%20place.%20In%20NGC2%2C%20AI%20is%20being%20tested%20where%20it%20can%20speed%20up%20specific%20tasks%20while%20leaving%20humans%20responsible%20for%20judgment%20calls.%20It's%20about%20figuring%20out%20where%20it%20actually%20helps%20and%20where%20it%20could%20unnecessarily%20add%20confusion%20or%20create%20problems.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOutside%20of%20Colorado%20Springs%20last%20month%2C%20the%20Army%20and%20its%20partners%20gathered%20for%20a%20massive%20NGC2%20exercise%20and%20conducted%20a%20series%20of%20fights%20between%20a%20blue%20team%20and%20a%20red%20team.%20The%20event%20was%20the%20latest%20stress%20test%20of%20the%20software%2C%20which%20has%20been%20developed%20by%20both%20the%204th%20ID%20and%20the%20Army's%2025th%20Infantry%20Division%20in%20Hawaii.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20exercise%2C%20soldiers%20described%20how%20NGC2%20is%20upgrading%20their%20communications%20on%20their%20laptops%2C%20tablets%2C%20and%20small%20smartphone-like%20devices%20worn%20on%20their%20chests%20and%20turning%20vehicles%20into%20mobile%20command%20posts.%20They%20also%20showed%20how%20they%20were%20using%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20mobile%20command%20post%20where%20soldiers%20were%20analyzing%20targets%2C%20AI%20was%20helping%20speed%20up%20the%20process%2C%20giving%20human%20operators%20clearer%20pictures%20of%20data%20before%20sending%20information%20up%20the%20chain%20for%20potential%20strikes.%20Soldiers%20described%20the%20AI%20as%20always%20working%20with%20humans%20in%20the%20loop%20and%20under%20guardrails%20similar%20to%20those%20they%20would%20apply%20to%20any%20new%20capability.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226720%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20soldier%20wearing%20camouflage%20looks%20through%20binoculars.%20Behind%20him%20is%20a%20line%20of%20green%20trees.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a2996acb19390180e4cf985%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224480%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESoldiers%20said%20AI%20had%20specific%20use%20cases%20in%20NGC2%20but%20had%20guardrails%20and%20human%20intervention.%3Cp%3EUS%20Army%20photo%20by%20Pfc.%20Jacob%20Cruz%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20key%20is%20reviewing%20AI%20as%20being%20yet%20another%20tool%20that's%20coming%20on%20board%2C%26quot%3B%20Hickox%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20soldiers%20still%20need%20to%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Efigure%20out%20how%20best%20to%20train%20and%20use%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETroops%20suggested%20that%20AI%20was%20most%20helpful%20for%20reducing%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Farmy-general-new-tech-no-more-hour-long-decision-meetings-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecognitive%20load%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20sorting%20intelligence%2C%20surveillance%2C%20reconnaissance%20information%20and%20targeting%20data%2C%20especially%20when%20the%20battlefield%20is%20full%20of%20information%20that%20needs%20to%20be%20digested%20and%20processed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20that%20potential%20is%20not%20new%2C%20the%20development%20of%20NGC2%20has%20suggested%20it%20could%20become%20more%20widespread%20as%20models%20are%20trained%20and%20soldiers%20become%20more%20accustomed%20to%20using%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20were%20to%20tell%20me%20I%20could%20use%20AI%20on%20the%20move%2C%26quot%3B%20Hickox%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20its%20use%20in%20the%20mobile%20command%20post%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20wouldn't%20have%20believed%20you%20probably%20eight%20months%20ago.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20could%20run%20through%20substantial%20amounts%20of%20data%20and%20then%20help%20identify%20and%20present%20potential%20targeting%20options.%20Soldiers%20could%20then%20double-check%20that%20output%20before%20deciding%20whether%20to%20pursue%20a%20strike.%20The%20process%20can%20move%20much%20faster%2C%20eliminating%20hours%20of%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESoldiers%20also%20believe%20that%20as%20AI%20becomes%20more%20trained%20on%20doctrine%20and%20information%2C%20agents%20could%20act%20as%20mentors.%20As%20younger%20troops%20who%20may%20be%20more%20comfortable%20with%20the%20technology%20enter%20service%2C%20they'd%20potentially%20see%20AI%20as%20a%20way%20to%20answer%20questions%20and%20solve%20problems.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20probably%20going%20to%20be%20flaws%20in%20it%2C%20but%20that's%20where%20we%20come%20in%20as%20humans%20being%20able%20to%20adjust%20and%20adapt%2C%26quot%3B%20Hickox%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EArmy%20leaders%20believe%20that%20AI-assisted%20capabilities%20will%20be%20needed%20in%20future%20wars%20wh