erial%20vehicles%20equipped%20with%20jet%20engines%20are%20carried%20by%20a%20truck%20during%20a%20military%20parade%20commemorating%20the%20anniversary%20of%20the%20Iran-Iraq%20War%20outside%20the%20Khomeini%20Shrine%20in%20the%20south%20of%20Tehran%2C%20Iran%2C%20on%20September%2021%2C%202024.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a26db612ab5f9757adda1e2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDrones%20with%20jet%20engines%20can%20travel%20much%20faster%20than%20those%20with%20propellers.%3Cp%3EMorteza%20Nikoubazl%2FNurPhoto%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20make%20this%20happen%2C%20Ukrainian%20companies%20are%20integrating%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-zelenskyy-drones-ai-russia-war-silicon-valley-defense-tech-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eartificial%20intelligence%3C%2Fa%3E%20into%20their%20interceptor%20drones.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESkyfall's%20next-generation%20interceptor%2C%20called%20the%20P1-Sun%20Long%2C%20uses%20AI%20to%20detect%20drones%20at%20roughly%20half%20a%20mile%2C%20aiding%20the%20operator%20if%20they%20can't%20see%20the%20target%2C%20the%20company%20representative%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20added%20that%20Skyfall%20is%20also%20developing%20an%20autonomous%20version%20of%20the%20P1-Sun%2C%20where%20the%20pilot%20will%20only%20need%20to%20press%20a%20button%20to%20start%20or%20cancel%20the%20mission%2C%20allowing%20them%20to%20oversee%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-developing-interceptor-drone-swarms-defend-against-russian-attacks-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eseveral%20interceptors%20simultaneously%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20development%20is%20part%20of%20a%20much%20larger%20effort%20across%20Ukraine's%20defense%20industry%20to%20create%20drone%20swarms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Wild%20Hornets%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-g