Watson%20will%20serve%20as%20president%20of%20the%20jury%20for%20the%20Feature%20Film%20Competition%20Program%20at%20the%2032nd%20Sarajevo%20Film%20Festival.%20She%20will%20also%20receive%20the%20Honorary%20Heart%20of%20Sarajevo%20at%20the%20festival%2C%20in%20recognition%20of%20her%20contribution%20to%20world%20cinema.%20Jovan%20Marjanovi%C4%87%2C%20director%20of%20the%20festival%20said%20Watson%20was%20an%20actress%20%E2%80%9Cwhose%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Leo%20Barraclough%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Judges%20are%20losing%20patience%20with%20lawyers'%20AI%20mistakes%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20judge's%20gavel.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a29a66159f798e5451f627d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20federal%20Mississippi%20judge%20issued%20sharply%20worded%20sanctions%20earlier%20this%20week%20after%20AI%20mistakes%20were%20found%20in%20lawyers'%20court%20filings.%3Cp%3EAtthapon%20Niyom%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAI%20hallucinations%20in%20court%20filings%20got%20lawyers%20on%20both%20sides%20kicked%20off%20a%20case.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20federal%20Mississippi%20judge%20also%20imposed%20a%20combined%20%248%2C000%20in%20fines%20on%20the%20four%20attorneys.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt%20shows%20how%20judges%20are%20taking%20a%20tougher%20stance%20on%20AI%20errors%20in%20filings%2C%20a%20legal%20expert%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EJudges%20are%20getting%20tired%20of%20cleaning%20up%20the%20AI%20slop%20oozing%20into%20their%20courtrooms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20latest%20example%20of%20their%20patience%20wearing%20thin%20can%20be%20found%20in%20Mississippi%2C%20where%20a%20federal%20judge%20brought%20the%20hammer%20down%20earlier%20this%20week%20on%20attorneys%20on%20both%20sides%20of%20a%20lawsuit%20after%20they%20admitted%20to%20submitting%20court%20filings%20containing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fincreasing-ai-hallucinations-fake-citations-court-records-data-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebogus%20citations%20generated%20by%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20sharply%20worded%20sanctions%20order%20issued%20Monday%2C%20US%20District%20Judge%20Sharion%20Aycock%20removed%20all%20four%20lawyers%20from%20the%20case%2C%20barred%20two%20from%20practicing%20before%20the%20court%20for%20two%20years%2C%20and%20imposed%20a%20combined%20%248%2C000%20in%20fines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20District%20Court%20for%20the%20Northern%20District%20of%20Mississippi%20%26quot%3Bis%20yet%20again%20'burdened%20with%20addressing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flawyers-legal-tech-companies-fight-ai-chatgpt-hallucinations-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%20hallucinations%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20court%20filings%2C'%26quot%3B%20Aycock%20wrote%20in%20the%2023-page%20order%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20case%20presents%20the%20Court%20with%20an%20unusual%20scenario%E2%80%94attorneys%20for%20both%20litigants%20engaged%20in%20similar%20sanctionable%20conduct.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20order%20reflects%20a%20growing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-hallucinations-court-filings-eve-dudley-debosier-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efrustration%20among%20US%20judges%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20lawyers%20who%20file%20court%20briefs%20with%20AI-generated%20errors%2C%20a%20legal%20expert%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20some%20earlier%20examples%20of%20the%20same%20behavior%2C%20offending%20attorneys%20were%20let%20off%20with%20a%20slap%20on%20the%20wrist%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mark%20Bartholomew%2C%20a%20University%20at%20Buffalo%20School%20of%20Law%20professor.%20%26quot%3BNow%20judges%20just%20don't%20buy%20it%20when%20a%20lawyer%20protests%20they%20had%20no%20idea%20that%20AI%20models%20can%20hallucinate%2C%20and%20they%20are%20willing%20to%20call%20such%20behavior%20out%20as%20bad%20faith.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAycock's%20sanctions%20stem%20from%20legal%20briefs%20filed%20by%20lawyers%20in%20the%20case%20involving%20a%20contractual%20dispute%20over%20legal%20fees%20between%20the%20plaintiff%2C%20Louisiana%20attorney%20Tom%20Withers%2C%20and%20the%20defendant%2C%20the%20Mississippi%20city%20of%20Aberdeen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20judge's%20order%2C%20Kathleen%20Wilson%2C%20an%20out-of-state%20attorney%20for%20Withers%2C%20admitted%20to%20using%20an%20AI%20tool%20to%20conduct%20legal%20research%2C%20while%20Kathryn%20Williams%2C%20an%20out-of-state%20lawyer%20for%20Aberdeen%2C%20owned%20up%20to%20using%20generative%20AI%20to%20draft%20a%20filing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNeither%20of%20them%20verified%20the%20legal%20authority%20output%20by%20AI%20before%20filing%20their%20briefs%2C%26quot%3B%20Aycock%20wrote.%20The%20judge%20continued%2C%20%26quot%3BTheir%20acts%20of%20relying%20on%20AI%20output%20without%20verification%20alone%20supports%20a%20finding%20that%20they%20acted%20in%20bad%20faith.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShauncey%20Ridgeway%20and%20Mark%20McClinton%2C%20the%20local%20counsel%20for%20the%20plaintiff%20and%20defendant%2C%20respectively%2C%20acknowledged%20they%20had%20not%20reviewed%20the%20filings%20before%20they%20were%20submitted%2C%20the%20order%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20four%20lawyers%20said%20they%20only%20learned%20that%20AI-hallucinated%20court%20cases%20were%20cited%20in%20their%20filings%20after%20the%20judge%20brought%20the%20issue%20to%20their%20attention%20late%20last%20year%2C%20according%20to%20Aycock's%20order%2C%20which%20said%20the%20lawyers%20apologized%20and%20%26quot%3Bexpressed%20embarrassment.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20discovery%20had%20prompted%20the%20court%20to%20stay%20the%20case%20and%20cancel%20the%20scheduled%20trial.%20And%20the%20attorneys'%20apologies%20did%20little%20to%20satisfy%20the%20judge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20an%20era%20of%20rampant%20unverified%20AI%20usage%20within%20the%20legal%20field%2C%20this%20case%20presents%20a%20prime%20example%20of%20the%20risk%20associated%20with%20serving%20as%20a%20rubberstamp%20when%20acting%20as%20local%20counsel%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20judge%20wrote%20in%20her%20Monday%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWilson%20and%20Williams%20were%20hit%20with%20the%20stiffest%20penalties%20%E2%80%94%20two-year%20suspensions%20from%20appearing%20before%20the%20court%20and%20fines%20of%20%242%2C500%20and%20%243%2C500%2C%20respectively.%20Ridgeway%20and%20McClinton%20were%20disqualified%20from%20the%20case%20and%20each%20fined%20%241%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20judge%20has%20given%20Withers%20and%20the%20city%20of%20Aberdeen%2060%20days%20to%20find%20new%20counsel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWilliams%20declined%20to%20comment%2C%20while%20the%20other%20attorneys%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment%20by%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20managing%20partner%20at%20Ridgeway's%20law%20firm%2C%20Christian%20%26amp%3B%20Small%20LLP%2C%20said%20the%20firm%20would%20%26quot%3Bcontinue%20to%20educate%20our%20team%20about%20the%20appropriate%20use%20of%20artificial%20intelligence%20tools%20when%20they%20can%20benefit%20our%20clients%2C%20and%20the%20absolute%20requirement%20that%20our%20lawyers%20verify%20all%20information%20in%20our%20filings%20is%20accurate%20and%20correct.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20many%20professions%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flaw-firm-cozen-oconnor-shares-best-practices-ai-tool-pilots-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elegal%20industry%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20rapidly%20embraced%20AI%20tools.%20According%20to%20the%202026%20Legal%20Industry%20Report%20by%20the%20business%20platform%208am%2C%2069%25%20of%20surveyed%20legal%20professionals%20reported%20using%20generative%20AI%20tools%20for%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20recent%20months%2C%20attorneys%20in%20several%20cases%20handled%20by%20top%20firms%20have%20come%20under%20scrutiny%20for%20their%20use%20of%20AI%20in%20the%20courtroom.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20law%20firms%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fincreasing-ai-hallucinations-fake-citations-court-records-data-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EEllis%20George%20and%20K%26amp%3BL%20Gates%3C%2Fa%3E%20were%20ordered%20by%20a%20judge%20to%20pay%20about%20%2431%2C000%20in%20sanctions%20after%20attorneys%20filed%20a%20brief%20containing%20made-up%20cases%20generated%20by%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20year%2C%20a%20partner%20at%20Wall%20Street%20law%20firm%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsullivan-and-cromwell-apologizes-ai-hallucinations-court-filing-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESullivan%20%26amp%3B%20Cromwell%3C%2Fa%3E%20apologized%20to%20a%20federal%20bankruptcy%20judge%20after%20submitting%20a%20court%20filing%20with%20AI%20hallucinations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBartholomew%2C%20the%20law%20professor%2C%20said%20he%20expects%20more%20lawyers%20to%20face%20sanctions%20from%20judges%20over%20AI-generated%20mistakes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20temptation%20is%20just%20too%20great%20for%20overworked%20lawyers%20looking%20for%20ways%20to%20cut%20corners%2C%26quot%3B%20Bartholomew%20said%2C%20explaining%20that%20until%20AI%20firms%20%26quot%3Bsolve%20the%20hallucination%20problem%2C%20there%20will%20be%20more%20of%20these%20cases%20and%20more%20sanctions.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmississippi-judge-removes-lawyers-lawsuit-ai-hallucinations-court-filings-2026-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1781170202000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a29a86e59f798e5451f6299%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmississippi-judge-removes-lawyers-lawsuit-ai-hallucinations-court-filings-2026-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20Mississippi%20federal%20judge%20removed%20all%20four%20lawyers%20from%20a%20case%2C%20barred%20two%20from%20practicing%20before%20the%20court%2C%20and%20issued%20%248%2C000%20in%20fines.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22nmusumeci%40businessinsider.com%20(Natalie%20Musumeci)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A99%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22He%20built%20tech%20to%20connect%20the%20Israeli%20army's%20data.%20Now%20he%20has%20%2414%20million%20from%20VCs%20to%20do%20it%20for%20companies.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222329%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Two%20men%20wearing%20Upriver%20shirts%20pose%20in%20front%20of%20a%20large%20Upriver%20logo%20on%20an%20office%20wall.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a21bd242e5a80cfe0503849%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221747%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIdo%20Bronstein%20and%20Omri%20Lifshitz.%3Cp%3EUpriver%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EIsraeli%20startup%20Upriver%20has%20raised%20%2414%20million%20to%20improve%20AI%20data%20management%20for%20companies.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20founders'%20military%20experience%20in%20data%20intelligence%20inspired%20Upriver's%20approach%20to%20business%20data.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EUpriver's%20agents%20streamline%20data%20pipelines%20and%20is%20used%20by%20customers%20like%20Unity%2C%20DMGT%2C%20and%20Nimble.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIdo%20Bronstein%20learned%20how%20to%20turn%20messy%20data%20into%20usable%20intelligence%20inside%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fisrael-losing-tech-workers-war-politics-cost-of-living-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EIsraeli%20military%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Now%20he%20wants%20to%20do%20the%20same%20for%20companies%20trying%20to%20make%20artificial%20intelligence%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUpriver%2C%20the%20startup%20he%20cofounded%20with%20Omri%20Lifschitz%2C%20has%20raised%20%2414%20million%20to%20help%20companies%20clean%20up%20and%20manage%20the%20business%20data%20that%20software%20tools%20need%20to%20work%20reliably.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EValley%20Capital%20and%20Hetz%20Ventures%20led%20the%20seed%20round%2C%20with%20participation%20from%20angel%20investors%2C%20including%20two%20of%20the%20founders%20of%20Cyera%2C%20the%20Israeli%20cybersecurity%20startup%2C%20last%20valued%20at%20%246%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThree%20years%20ago%2C%20Bronstein%20was%20serving%20in%20an%20elite%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-israeli-cybersecurity-startup-is-already-valued-at-400-million-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eintelligence%20unit%20of%20the%20Israel%20Defense%20Forces%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20where%20he%20built%20software%20to%20turn%20raw%20data%20from%20multiple%20sources%20into%20information%20officers%20could%20use.%20He%20later%20managed%20a%20team%20of%20engineers%20that%20scaled%20that%20infrastructure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBronstein%20said%20the%20problem%20was%20similar%20to%20the%20one%20now%20facing%20data%20teams%20inside%20large%20companies.%20They%20also%20need%20to%20gather%20scattered%20information%2C%20make%20it%20usable%2C%20and%20deliver%20it%20to%20the%20people%20and%20systems%20that%20depend%20on%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECompanies%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fteradata-pauses-raises-employee-compensation-ai-budget-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Espending%20heavily%20to%20deploy%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20those%20systems%20are%20only%20as%20useful%20as%20the%20data%20that%20feeds%20them.%20When%20that%20data%20is%20poor%20quality%20or%20spread%20across%20disconnected%20systems%2C%20Bronstein%20said%2C%20the%20tools%20may%20not%20perform%20as%20they%20should.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20typical%20fix%20has%20been%20to%20hire%20more%20people%20to%20maintain%20the%20underlying%20data%2C%20Bronstein%20said.%20Upriver%20is%20betting%20there's%20a%20better%20way%20to%20scale%3A%20using%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-coding-agents-tools-software-engineering-jobs-future-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eautonomous%20agents%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20take%20on%20some%20of%20that%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20large%20companies%20have%20complicated%20data%20setups.%20A%20customer%20might%20pull%20data%20through%20tools%20like%20Fivetran%2C%20store%20it%20in%20Snowflake%2C%20orchestrate%20with%20Airflow%2C%20and%20visualize%20with%20tools%20like%20Tableau.%20Upriver's%20agents%20plug%20into%20those%20systems%20and%20study%20how%20information%20moves%20through%20them.%20They%20can%20spot%20data%20that%20is%20incomplete%2C%20duplicated%2C%20or%20unreliable%2C%20and%20then%20help%20maintain%20the%20pipelines%20that%20move%20that%20data%20between%20applications.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBronstein%20describes%20the%20software%20as%20a%20kind%20of%20superhuman%20data%20engineer.%20Rather%20than%20asking%20teams%20to%20manually%20check%20data%20quality%2C%20rebuild%20pipelines%2C%20or%20prepare%20datasets%20for%20tools%2C%20Upriver%20uses%20agents%20to%20perform%20some%20of%20that%20work%20on%20their%20behalf.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20says%20its%20software%20is%20already%20used%20by%20Unity%2C%20DMGT%2C%20and%20Nimble%2C%20and%20that%20it%20has%20partnerships%20with%20Databricks%20and%20Snowflake.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20obvious%20question%20for%20Upriver%20is%3A%20why%20would%20Snowflake%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fceo-databricks-glean-ai-automation-overestimate-ali-ghodsi-arvind-jain-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDatabricks%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20or%20another%20data%20giant%20not%20own%20this%20problem%20themselves%3F%20Bronstein%20argues%20that%20those%20platforms%20are%20part%20of%20the%20infrastructure%20Upriver%20is%20meant%20to%20work%20across%2C%20rather%20than%20replace.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUpriver%20may%20compete%20more%20directly%20with%20startups%20trying%20to%20automate%20the%20work%20of%20data%20teams%20with%20agents.%20Ardent%20AI%2C%20Definity%2C%20Databahn%2C%20and%20Matillion%20have%20all%20pitched%20versions%20of%20agentic%20data%20engineering%2C%20while%20Snowflake%20and%20Microsoft%20have%20already%20moved%20to%20buy%20startups%20in%20the%20space%2C%20acquiring%20TensorStax%20and%20Osmos%2C%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBronstein%20and%20Lifshitz%20met%20in%20Talpiot%2C%20an%20elite%20Israeli%20military%20program%20for%20technically%20gifted%20recruits%20who%20study%20advanced%20subjects%20while%20working%20on%20defense%20technology%20and%20research.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETalpiot%20has%20also%20become%20a%20well-known%20feeder%20into%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fisraeli-entrepreneurs-leaders-in-tech-startups-due-to-national-character-2019-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EIsrael's%20startup%20sector%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Its%20graduates%20include%20Check%20Point%20cofounder%20Marius%20Nacht%3B%20three%20of%20Wiz's%20four%20founders%2C%20Assaf%20Rappaport%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwiz-founder-google-acquisition-cloud-security-in-ai-age-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAmi%20Luttwak%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20Yinon%20Costica%3B%20and%20founders%20of%20companies%20including%20Cyera%2C%20Classiq%2C%20and%20Via.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUpriver%20is%20betting%20that%20the%20same%20kind%20of%20training%20that%20produced%20some%20of%20Israel's%20best-known%20startups%20can%20be%20applied%20to%20a%20more%20basic%20corporate%20problem%3A%20making%20sure%20companies%20can%20trust%20the%20data%20their%20tools%20depend%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fisrael-startup-upriver-raises-14-million-ai-data-engineering-2026-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%