og%20Is%E2%80%9D)%20on%20the%20heels%20of%20its%20world%20premiere%20at%20the%20Thessaloniki%20Documentary%20Festival.%20Broadcasters%20and%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22John%20Hopewell%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20millennial%20who%20hit%20'Coast%20FIRE'%20says%20the%20first%20step%20to%20financial%20independence%20has%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20number-crunching%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221226%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22andy%20hill%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a28c1bea74097c573988873%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22817%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAndy%20Hill%20quit%20his%20corporate%20job%20in%202020%20to%20focus%20on%20his%20own%20business%2C%20Marriage%20Kids%20and%20Money.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Andy%20Hill%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAndy%20Hill%20achieved%20%26quot%3BCoast%20FIRE%26quot%3B%20in%202020%2C%20allowing%20him%20to%20quit%20his%20corporate%20job.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20says%20the%20first%20step%20to%20financial%20independence%20isn't%20numbers-related%3A%20'do%20some%20dreaming.'%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThink%20about%20your%20dream%20life%20so%20that%20financial%20independence%20becomes%20more%20than%20an%20arbitrary%20number.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20most%20people%20think%20about%20financial%20independence%2C%20they%20think%20about%20spreadsheets%2C%20net%20worth%20projections%2C%20and%20savings%20rates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAndy%20Hill%20thinks%20they%20should%20start%20somewhere%20else.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20received%20a%20%245%20million%20check%20today%2C%20what%20would%20you%20stop%20doing%20immediately%3F%26quot%3B%20Hill%2C%20a%20family%20finance%20coach%20who%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-reach-coast-fire-financial-independence-investing-index-funds-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereached%20%26quot%3BCoast%20FIRE%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewith%20his%20wife%2C%20Nicole%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHill%20believes%20this%20thought%20experiment%20can%20reveal%20more%20about%20your%20goals%20than%20any%20retirement%20calculator.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20your%20answer%20is%2C%20'I'd%20quit%20my%20job%20immediately%2C'%20then%20maybe%20that's%20a%20signal%20that%20you%20don't%20like%20your%20job%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BCould%20you%20find%20a%20different%20job%20that%20pays%20the%20same%20but%20offers%20a%20better%20environment%3F%20Could%20you%20work%20fewer%20hours%3F%20Could%20you%20make%20changes%20before%20reaching%20financial%20independence%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Hill%2C%20dreaming%20comes%20before%20number-crunching.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20very%20first%20step%20would%20be%20to%20do%20some%20dreaming%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20know%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20time%20we're%20looking%20at%20these%20numbers%2C%20but%20I%20really%20think%20you%20should%20step%20back%20and%20say%2C%20'What%20would%20I%20do%20if%20I%20hit%20financial%20independence%3F%20What%20would%20I%20do%20if%20I%20hit%20Coast%20FIRE%3F%20How%20would%20my%20life%20be%20different%3F'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThink%20about%20what%20your%20ideal%20week%20looks%20like%2C%20and%20write%20it%20down.%20That%20way%2C%20financial%20independence%20becomes%20more%20than%20just%20an%20arbitrary%20number%2C%20he%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20just%20focus%20on%20the%20numbers%2C%20it%20loses%20purpose.%20It%20loses%20a%20why.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20you've%20identified%20what%20you're%20working%20toward%2C%20then%20you%20can%20run%20the%20numbers.%20Keep%20in%20mind%20that%20financial%20independence%20doesn't%20have%20to%20mean%20saving%20more%20than%20half%20of%20your%20income%20and%20accumulating%20millions%20of%20dollars.%20There%20are%20offshoots%20of%20the%20FIRE%20(financial%20independence%2C%20retire%20early)%20movement%20that%20can%20feel%20more%20attainable%2C%20such%20as%20%26quot%3BCoast%20FIRE%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20the%20Hills%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftraditional-fire-vs-coast-fire-financial-independence-retire-early-investing-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epivoted%20to%20after%20getting%20burnt%20out%20chasing%20traditional%20FIRE%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFIRE%20itself%20can%20be%20a%2015-%2C%2020-%2C%20or%2025-year%20journey%2C%26quot%3B%20Hill%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20depending%20on%20your%20income%2C%20it%20might%20not%20be%20the%20most%20comfortable%20journey%20for%20a%20lot%20of%20people.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECoast%20FIRE%20still%20involves%20front-loading%20your%20investments%2C%20but%20the%20goal%20isn't%20to%20stop%20working%20altogether.%20The%20goal%20is%20to%20build%20a%20portfolio%20large%20enough%20to%20grow%20to%20your%20retirement%20target%20on%20its%20own%20through%20compound%20interest.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20you%20reach%20your%20Coast%20FIRE%20number%2C%20you%20can%20reduce%20or%20stop%20retirement%20contributions%20and%20redirect%20that%20money%20toward%20other%20priorities%2C%20whether%20that's%20spending%20more%20on%20experiences%2C%20working%20fewer%20hours%2C%20changing%20careers%2C%20or%20starting%20a%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20Hills%2C%20that%20number%20was%20about%20%24550%2C000%20invested%20by%20age%2040.%20Assuming%20a%206%25%20annual%20rate%20of%20return%2C%20Hill%20estimated%20that%20the%20balance%20could%20grow%20to%20roughly%20%242%20million%20by%20retirement%20age.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20was%20plenty%20for%20us%20to%20live%20on%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20those%20projections%20aren't%20guaranteed%2C%20and%20it's%20important%20to%20account%20for%20inflation%2C%20fund%20expenses%2C%20and%20advisory%20fees%20when%20estimating%20future%20returns.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHill%2C%20who%20quit%20his%20corporate%20job%20in%202020%20to%20focus%20on%20growing%20his%20financial%20education%20business%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarriagekidsandmoney.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EMarriage%20Kids%20and%20Money%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20regularly%20checks%20his%20family's%20progress%20using%20compound-interest%20and%20Coast%20FIRE%20calculators.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20important%20to%20continually%20check%20in%20over%20time%20to%20make%20sure%20you're%20still%20on%20track%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20if%20the%20numbers%20change%2C%20there's%20nothing%20wrong%20with%20adjusting%20the%20plan.%20%26quot%3BIf%20we%20find%20we're%20not%20on%20track%20anymore%2C%20we'll%20go%20back%20and%20continue%20to%20add%20to%20our%20IRAs%20so%20that%20we're%20continuing%20to%20have%20a%20comfortable%20retirement.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsteps-to-achieve-financial-independence-retire-early-coast-fire-2026-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1781169302000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a28c7e0b19390180e4ced63%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsteps-to-achieve-financial-independence-retire-early-coast-fire-2026-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Andy%20Hill%2C%20a%20finance%20coach%20and%20a%20millennial%20who%20hit%20FIRE%20said%20there's%20a%20step%20that%20comes%20before%20running%20the%20numbers%20when%20aiming%20for%20financial%20independence.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22kelkins%40businessinsider.com%20(Kathleen%20Elkins)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%227%20million%20student-loan%20borrowers%20will%20soon%20need%20to%20take%20action%20%E2%80%94%20or%20be%20put%20on%20the%20most%20expensive%20repayment%20plan%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227008%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22College%20graduates%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a284dcb208d75cc7b792727%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224672%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EStudent-loan%20borrowers%20on%20the%20SAVE%20plan%20will%20soon%20receive%20notices%20with%20a%20deadline%20to%20transfer%20to%20a%20new%20repayment%20plan.%3Cp%3Enirat%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EStudent-loan%20borrowers%20on%20SAVE%20will%20receive%20notices%20to%20find%20a%20new%20plan%20beginning%20in%20July.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIf%20they%20do%20not%20take%20action%2C%20they'll%20automatically%20be%20placed%20in%20the%20most%20expensive%20plan.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBorrowers%20will%20be%20given%20a%2090-day%20timeframe%20to%20make%20a%20decision.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EMore%20expensive%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-student-loan-debt-repayment-overhaul-july-changes-borrowers-save-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Estudent-loan%20payments%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20coming.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeginning%20July%201%2C%20the%20Department%20of%20Education%20will%20notify%20student-loan%20borrowers%20enrolled%20in%20the%20SAVE%20plan%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsave-plan-student-loan-borrowers-need-more-time-repayment-debt-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etheir%20deadline%20to%20transfer%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20a%20new%20repayment%20plan.%20It%20follows%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20elimination%20of%20SAVE%2C%20which%20gave%20borrowers%20cheaper%20monthly%20payments%20and%20a%20shorter%20timeline%20to%20debt%20relief.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20email%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsave-plan-student-loan-borrowers-kicked-off-new-email-repayment-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESAVE%20borrowers%20received%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20reviewed%20by%20Business%20Insider%2C%20said%20that%20borrowers%20who%20do%20not%20select%20a%20new%20plan%20in%20the%2090-day%20timeframe%20they%20are%20given%20will%20automatically%20be%20placed%20in%20either%20the%20standard%20repayment%20plan%20or%20the%20new%20tiered%20standard%20plan%2C%20both%20of%20which%20are%20more%20expensive%20than%20the%20existing%20income-driven%20repayment%20plans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYour%20monthly%20payment%20amount%20will%20most%20likely%20go%20up%20if%20you%20are%20enrolled%20in%20either%20of%20these%20plans%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20department's%20email%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Caside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20will%20Trump's%20student-loan%20changes%20affect%20you%3F%20Are%20you%20preparing%20for%20higher%20monthly%20payments%20or%20changing%20your%20educational%20plans%3F%20Share%20your%20story%20by%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2F7Td2yVsmvM31yKsT6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efilling%20out%20this%20form%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20reach%20out%20to%20this%20reporter%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aasheffey%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Easheffey%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3A%2520asheffey%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Faside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20tiered%20standard%20plan%2C%20which%20will%20become%20available%20after%20July%201%2C%20would%20require%20borrowers%20to%20repay%20their%20loans%20in%20full%20over%20a%20period%20based%20on%20the%20amount%20of%20their%20principal%20balance%2C%20with%20a%20minimum%20payment%20of%20%2450%20a%20month.%20The%20new%20Repayment%20Assistance%20Plan%2C%20also%20available%20in%20July%2C%20would%20calculate%20a%20borrower's%20monthly%20payment%20based%20on%20their%20adjusted%20gross%20income.%20It's%20more%20expensive%20than%20existing%20income-based%20plans%2C%20which%20set%20aside%20a%20portion%20of%20a%20borrower's%20monthly%20expenses%20and%20calculate%20their%20monthly%20payment%20based%20on%20the%20lower%20amount.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBorrowers%20are%20not%20required%20to%20take%20any%20action%20until%20they%20receive%20notices%20informing%20them%20of%20their%20deadline%20to%20transfer%20to%20new%20plans.%20Some%20have%20already%20said%20that%20their%20payments%20are%20projected%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-borrowers-scramble-save-debt-repayment-plan-trump-confusion-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esurge%20by%20hundreds%20of%20dollars%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20RAP%2C%20which%20is%20intended%20to%20be%20the%20more%20affordable%20option.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%2060%20Democratic%20lawmakers%20recently%20urged%20the%20Department%20of%20Education%20to%20place%20SAVE%20borrowers%20in%20the%20cheapest%20plan%2C%20rather%20than%20the%20most%20expensive%20one%2C%20if%20they%20do%20not%20take%20action%20before%20their%20given%20deadline.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20mitigate%20the%20potentially%20devastating%20financial%20impact%20of%20this%20transition%2C%20ED%20should%20automatically%20enroll%20every%20borrower%20currently%20in%20the%20SAVE%20forbearance%20in%20the%20lowest%20cost%20repayment%20plan%20currently%20available%20to%20that%20borrower%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20lawmakers%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20the%20new%20repayment%20plans%2C%20other%20provisions%20of%20Trump's%20%26quot%3Bbig%20beautiful%26quot%3B%20spending%20legislation%20will%20soon%20go%20into%20effect%2C%20including%20new%20borrowing%20caps%20on%20advanced%20degrees%20and%20changes%20to%20the%20amounts%20parents%20can%20borrow%20for%20their%20kids'%20education.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENicholas%20Kent%2C%20the%20department's%20under%20secretary%2C%20said%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-student-loan-debt-repayment-overhaul-final-rule-new-plans-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ein%20an%20April%20press%20release%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20%26quot%3Bchanges%20will%20ensure%20students%20continue%20to%20have%20the%20access%20that%20they%20need%20for%20federal%20student%20loans%2C%20while%20helping%20prevent%20borrowers%20from%20taking%20on%20unmanageable%20debt%20levels%20that%20they%20may%20never%20be%20able%20to%20repay.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHave%20a%20story%20to%20share%20about%20student%20loans%3F%20Contact%20this%20reporter%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3A%2520asheffey%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Easheffey%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsave-plan-student-loan-borrowers-most-expensive-repayment-trump-changes-2026-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1781169301000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a284dddea70485acd8b236e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsave-plan-student-loan-borrowers-most-expensive-repayment-trump-changes-2026-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Student-loan%20borrowers%20on%20the%20SAVE%20plan%20will%20soon%20receive%20notices%20to%20transfer%20to%20a%20new%20plan.%20If%20they%20don't%20take%20action%2C%20bills%20could%20be%20even%20higher.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22asheffey%40businessinsider.com%20(Ayelet%20Sheffey)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Trinamool%20Exodus%20Reflects%20Public%20Dissatisfaction'%3A%20Minister%20Jabs%20Mamata%20Banerjee%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22CR%20Patil%20alleged%20that%20leaders%20who%20once%20projected%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20as%20politically%20invincible%20are%20now%20abandoning%20the%20party%20because%20they%20fear%20its%20declining%20public%20support%20and%20uncertain%20future.%22%2C%22published%22%3A1781169242000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftrinamool-exodus-ref