h%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author%20wearing%20a%20lavender%20dress%20while%20pregnant%2C%20standing%20on%20a%20dock.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a2837ecea70485acd8b195e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221134%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20joined%20a%20due%20date%20group%20when%20she%20was%20pregnant.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Jessica%20Lawlor%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EWhen%20I%20found%20out%20I%20was%20pregnant%2C%20I%20joined%20an%20online%20due%20date%20group.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWe%20started%20as%20strangers%20and%20became%20friends%2C%20helping%20each%20other%20through%20pregnancy%2C%20birth%2C%20and%20more.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ENow%2C%20years%20later%2C%20we%20still%20talk%20daily.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20say%20it%20takes%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillennial-moms-tiktok-parenting-trends-it-takes-village-raise-children-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evillage%20to%20raise%20a%20child%3C%2Fa%3E%3B%20I%20found%20my%20village%20in%20the%20form%20of%2046%20strangers%20in%20an%20online%20due%20date%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20due%20date%20group%20%E2%80%94%20or%20a%20DDG%20for%20the%20acronym-loving%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftoxic-mom-group-judgment-why-i-left-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emom%20community%20online%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20is%20a%20group%20chat%20of%20women%20who%20are%20pregnant%20whose%20due%20dates%20are%20in%20the%20same%20month.%20Sometimes%20the%20group%20forms%20in%20large%20Facebook%20communities%20with%20thousands%20of%20members%2C%20or%20in%20private%20subreddits%20where%20you're%20required%20to%20upload%20a%20dated%20ultrasound%20as%20proof%20of%20pregnancy%20to%20gain%20entry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20due%20date%20group%20I%20joined%20shortly%20after%20receiving%20a%20positive%20pregnancy%20test%20in%20September%202022%20originated%20in%20a%20Facebook%20group%2C%20then%20moved%20to%20an%20app%20called%20BFF.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20one%20point%2C%20there%20were%20more%20than%2060%20women%20in%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcollege-parent-group-chats-gen-x-gen-z-surveillance-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egroup%20chat%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20by%20the%20time%20we%20gave%20birth%2C%20it%20was%20me%20and%2046%20others%2C%20and%20we%20officially%20%26quot%3Bclosed%26quot%3B%20the%20group%20to%20maintain%20connection%20and%20privacy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENearly%20four%20years%20later%2C%20we%20still%20chat%20every%20single%20day%20%E2%80%94%20and%20many%20of%20us%20have%20met%20IRL%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22599070e7-5d21-4f06-ba76-4892715ddd16%5C%22%3EI%20found%20a%20mom%20community%20of%2046%20strangers%20from%20around%20the%20country%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20navigating%20the%20fertility%20side%20of%20social%20media%20while%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fartificial-insemination-got-pregnant-cheap-after-years-trying-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etrying%20to%20conceive%3C%2Fa%3E%20(TTC%2C%20if%20we're%20continuing%20with%20the%20acronyms)%2C%20finally%20joining%20a%20due%20date%20group%20felt%20like%20a%20rite%20of%20passage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20watched%20as%20women%20in%20the%20TTC%20Facebook%20group%20I%20participated%20in%20graduated%20to%20mom%20Facebook%20groups.%20They'd%20rave%20about%20their%20due%20date%20group%20chats%2C%20often%20announcing%20the%20babies'%20births%20with%20a%20photo%20of%20their%20newborns%20wearing%20the%20same%20cute%20outfit%20or%20sharing%20details%20of%20a%20group%20trip%20they'd%20taken%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFind%20your%20due%20date%20group!%26quot%3B%20their%20posts%20urged.%20I%20yearned%20for%20that%20sort%20of%20connection.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20joined%20%E2%80%94%20and%20quickly%20became%20enamored%20with%20%E2%80%94%20my%20group%20of%20June%202023%20moms.%20My%20phone%20buzzed%20all%20day%20as%20we%20got%20to%20know%20one%20another%20on%20BFF%2C%20where%20we've%20organized%20the%20chat%20into%20nearly%2050%20rooms%20spanning%20different%20topics%20of%20parenthood%20and%20personal%20interests.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f5ec8177-4df1-4746-ba7f-c0750aaf4575%5C%22%3EThe%20group%20became%20a%20lifeline%20during%20pregnancy%20and%20postpartum%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20throes%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftraveling-first-trimester-pregnancy-tips-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efirst%20trimester%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20we've%20been%20through%20it%20all%20together%20%E2%80%94%20gender%20reveals%2C%20baby%20showers%2C%20giving%20birth%2C%20sleepless%20nights%2C%20birthday%20party%20planning%2C%20cancer%20diagnoses%2C%20relationship%20ups%20and%20downs%2C%20losses%2C%20subsequent%20pregnancies%2C%20and%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20group%20especially%20shone%20in%20June%202023%2C%20when%20most%20of%20us%20gave%20birth%2C%20and%20during%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmultigenerational-house-living-with-mom-pregnancy-saved-me-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eearly%20postpartum%20days%3C%2Fa%3E.%20We%20were%20all%20on%20high%20alert%20for%20announcements%20of%20water%20breaking%20or%20planned%20induction%20or%20C-section%20dates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENearly%20every%20day%2C%20we%20celebrated%20a%20baby%20being%20born%3B%20sometimes%20two%20or%20three%20in%20a%20single%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20babies%20arrived%2C%20no%20matter%20the%20time%20of%20day%20(or%20more%20realistically%2C%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20night)%2C%20someone%20was%20online%20to%20lend%20an%20ear.%20It%20was%20nice%20to%20never%20feel%20alone%2C%20especially%20while%20feeding%20and%20rocking%20a%20baby%20in%20a%20dark%20room.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20wasn't%20all%20serious%2C%20though%3B%20on%20Friday%20nights%2C%20the%20chat%20lit%20up%20with%20what%20we%20called%20%26quot%3BFriday%20night%20polls%2C%26quot%3B%20one-upping%20each%20other%20with%20wilder%20and%20wilder%20questions%2C%20learning%20hilarious%20tidbits%20about%20each%20other%2C%20our%20marriages%2C%20and%20our%20families%2C%20along%20the%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstarting-neighborhood-book-club-to-make-real-friends-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebook%20club%3C%2Fa%3E%20formed.%20We%20hosted%20holiday%20gift%20exchanges%20on%20Zoom.%20A%20Fantasy%20Football%20league%20provided%20friendly%20competition%20during%20the%20NFL%20season.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20summer%20of%202024%2C%20just%20after%20our%20babies%20turned%20one%2C%2014%20of%20us%20met%20in%20person%20for%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkid-free-vacation-husband-change-fatherhood-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ekid-free%20weekend%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20North%20Carolina.%20We%20spent%20a%20glorious%20few%20days%20at%20a%20beautiful%20house%20on%20Lake%20Norman%2C%20sitting%20in%20the%20sunshine%20with%20a%20glass%20of%20wine%2C%20excited%20to%20simply%20be%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2230484099-98c6-403a-b1f0-3a061155d4ed%5C%22%3EThese%20friendships%20are%20real%20%E2%80%94%20and%20lasting%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20women%20are%20no%20longer%20strangers.%20Over%20the%20years%2C%20we've%20become%20more%20than%20casual%20acquaintances%20who%20met%20online%3B%20our%20bond%20runs%20deep.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20can%20tell%20you%20the%20names%20of%20the%20babies%20in%20the%20group%2C%20along%20with%20their%20siblings.%20I%20know%20who%20is%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstay-at-home-mom-making-1500-weekly-from-side-hustles-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estay-at-home%20mom%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20who%20is%20a%20working%20mom.%20I%20know%20who%20is%20planning%20a%20trip%20to%20Disney%20World%20next%20month.%20I%20know%20who%20wants%20to%20have%20more%20kids%20and%20whose%20families%20are%20complete.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20our%20babies%20have%20grown%20%E2%80%94%20the%20June%202023%20babies%20are%20now%20turning%20three!%20%E2%80%94%20the%20chat%20has%20evolved%20from%20trading%20feeding%20tips%20and%20venting%20about%20sleep%20deprivation%20to%20navigating%20toddler%20tantrums%20and%20potty%20training.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20chat%20isn't%20as%20active%20as%20in%20the%20early%20days%2C%20and%20some%20members%20have%20naturally%20dropped%20off%2C%20we're%20still%20extremely%20close%20%E2%80%94%20and%20many%20of%20us%20talk%20daily.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe've%20gone%20on%20to%20support%20one%20another%20through%20second%20(and%20even%20third!)%20pregnancies.%20These%20women%20were%20there%20for%20me%20during%20the%20most%20chaotic%2C%20messy%2C%20and%20beautiful%20time%20of%20my%20life%20%E2%80%94%20and%20I%20count%20some%20of%20them%20as%20real-life%20best%20friends%20these%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20welcomed%20my%20second%20baby%20in%20January%2C%20and%20yep%20%E2%80%94%20I%20joined%20another%20due%20date%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20village%20continues%20to%20grow.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpregnancy-due-date-group-chat-friendship-2026-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1781169062000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a2837ecea70485acd8b195e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpregnancy-due-date-group-chat-friendship-2026-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22My%20online%20due%20date%20group%20of%2040%2B%20strangers%20has%20been%20a%20lifeline%20as%20a%20first-time%20mom.%20Four%20years%20later%2C%20we%20still%20chat%20every%20day.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Jessica%20Lawlor)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Cathie%20Wood's%20latest%20big%20bet%20on%20Elon%20Musk%20is%20about%20to%20pay%20off%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226850%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Cathie%20Wood%20speaks%20at%20a%20conference%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a29c51bbfa7967f4b911b33%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224566%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECathie%20Wood%20founded%20ARK%20Invest%20more%20than%2010%20years%20ago.%3Cp%3EBloomberg%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ECathie%20Wood's%20ARK%20Invest%20became%20the%20North%20Star%20for%20growth-obsessed%20retail%20traders%20during%20the%20pandemic.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20reputation%20of%20the%20firm%20and%20its%20founder%20took%20a%20hit%20when%20inflation%20and%20interest%20rates%20spiked%2C%20as%20performance%20fell.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBut%20ARK%20Invest%20kept%20its%20focus%20on%20%26quot%3Bdisruptive%26quot%3B%20companies%2C%20and%20the%20coming%20wave%20of%20mega%20IPOs%20should%20be%20a%20boon.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20Elon%20Musk's%20biggest%20advocates%20could%20soon%20be%20rewarded%2C%20again%2C%20for%20her%20conviction.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EARK%20Invest's%20Cathie%20Wood%20made%20a%20name%20for%20herself%20because%20of%20her%20unflinching%20trust%20in%20Musk%2C%20Tesla%2C%20and%20a%20portfolio%20of%20pioneering%20tech%20companies%2C%20even%20as%20rising%20interest%20rates%20crushed%20growth%20stocks%20and%20turned%20her%20flagship%20fund%20from%20a%20pandemic%20darling%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Ffunds%2Fcathie-wood-ark-invest-wealth-destroyed-tech-stocks-morningstar-arkk-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eso-called%20wealth%20destroyer.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20the%20coming%20SpaceX%20IPO%20%E2%80%94%20which%20is%20the%20biggest%20holding%20in%20Wood's%20%241%20billion%20internal%20venture%20fund%20%E2%80%94%20could%20become%20the%20clearest%20vindication%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eof%20an%20investing%20style%20hyper-focused%20on%20%26quot%3Bdisruptive%26quot%3B%20technologies%20and%20little%20else.%20The%20fund%20first%20bought%20into%20the%20company%20in%20late%202023%2C%20filings%20show%2C%20when%20the%20company%20was%20valued%20at%20under%20%24200%20billion.%20It%20added%20to%20its%20position%20in%202025%20and%20gained%20additional%20exposure%20through%20its%20stake%20in%20xAI%2C%20which%20merged%20with%20the%20rocket%20ship%20company%20earlier%20this%20year.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspacex-ipo-why-investors-have-to-buy-spcx-elon-musk-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESpaceX's%20IPO%20is%20targeted%20%3C%2Fa%3Efor%20a%20%241.75%20trillion%20valuation.%3Cstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3EThe%20fund's%20other%20top%20holdings%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-anthropic-ai-ipo-spacex-stocks-stock-market-investing-trade-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EOpenAI%20and%20Anthropic%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20are%20also%20expected%20to%20follow%20SpaceX%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Einto%20the%20public%20markets%2C%20potentially%20providing%20another%20windfall%20for%20the%20manager%20and%20its%20backers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20the%20convergence%20of%20a%20lifetime%2C%26quot%3B%20Wood%20said%20on%20a%20recent%20YouTube%20stream%20where%20she%20mentioned%20developments%20on%20the%20moon%20and%20Mars%20as%20a%20part%20of%20her%20long-term%20view%20on%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20also%20a%20chance%20for%20ARK%2C%20which%20manages%20roughly%20%2416%20billion%2C%20to%20prove%20its%20unorthodox%20worldview%20can%20once%20again%20generate%20eye-popping%20returns.%20It's%20a%20manager%20known%20for%20%26quot%3Bhigh%20conviction%20in%20every%20one%20of%20its%20holdings%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Robby%20Greengold%2C%20an%20analyst%20at%20Morningstar%20who%20covers%20ARK%2C%20and%20a%20focus%20on%20companies%20with%20a%20high%20potential%20for%20both%20success%20and%20failure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20range%20of%20outcomes%20is%20wide%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222cd5665c-43f2-4001-90ff-3eb8d3c09ff5%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EQueen%20of%20Reddit%20traders%20to%20big%20losses%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ERoughly%20five%20years%20ago%2C%20a%20Business%20Insider%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcathie-wood-profile-ark-invest-etf-rise-success-following-tesla-2021-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eprofile%20of%20Wood%3C%2Fa%3E%20noted%20that%20the%20tech-focused%20investor%20had%20won%20the%20hearts%20and%20assets%20of%20%26quot%3Bmemelord%20traders%20and%20boomer%20investors%20alike.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20high%20point%20for%20Wood's%20public%20image%20and%20ARK%20Invest%2C%20which%20Wood%20started%20in%202014%20after%20a%20stint%20at%20AllianceBernstein.%20Since%20delivering%20returns%20of%20more%20than%20150%25%20in%202020%20and%20raising%20billions%20in%202021%2C%20the%20firm's%20flagship%20ETFs'%20assets%20have%20dropped%20by%20roughly%20two-thirds%2C%20thanks%20to%20a%2067%25%20loss%20in%202022%2C%20when%20inflation%20brought%20on%20by%20government%20stimulus%20during%20the%20pandemic%20forced%20central%20banks%20to%20increase%20interest%20rates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20ARK%20has%20always%20kept%20a%20long-term%20view%2C%20and%20the%20wave%20of%20mega%20IPOs%20on%20the%20horizon%20has%20provided%20a%20%26quot%3Bvalidation%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20firm's%20ultra-long-term%20view%2C%20said%20Brett%20Winton%2C%20the%20firm's%20chief%20futurist%2C%20in%20an%20interview%20with%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20pre-COVID%20public%20report%20from%20ARK%20%E2%80%94%20the%20firm%20produces%20a%20tremendous%20amount%20of%20public%20research%2C%20one%20of%20the%20reasons%20it%20endeared%20itself%20with%20Reddit-based%20retail%20traders%20during%20the%20pandemic%20%E2%80%94%20states%20early%20on%20that%20%26quot%3BAI%20is%20going%20to%20change%20the%20way%20that%20software%20is%20written%2C%26quot%3B%20Winton%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20five%20years%20later%2C%20it's%20happening%2C%20and%20as%20it%20turns%20out%2C%20that%20is%20a%20multi-trillion%20dollar%20opportunity%2C%20and%20it's%20being%20realized%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20as%20the%20firm's%20public%20stock%20holdings%20were%20taking%20a%20beating%20in%202022%2C%20the%20manager%20was%20focused%20on%20gaining%20greater%20access%20and%20exposure%20to%20the%20most%20cutting-edge%20(and%20cash-burning)%20companies.%20ARK%20launched%20its%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fark-venture-fund-cathie-wood-ai-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%20interval%20venture%20fund%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20year.%20The%20fund%20also%20has%20stakes%20in%20prediction%20market%20Kalshi%20and%20next-gen%20computing%20company%20Tenstorrent%20and%20has%20averaged%20a%2029%25%20gain%20each%20year%20since%20it%20launched.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e21f0f42-7b7a-40ff-b1ce-d8afa99ab44d%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20convergence%20around%20Musk%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETasha%20Keeney%2C%20the%20firm's%20director%20of%20investment%20analysis%2C%20doesn't%20think%20of%20SpaceX%20as%20a%20tech%20company%20or%20telecomms%20company%20in%20the%20way%20sell-side%20researchers%20and%20traditional%20investors%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20classification%20system%20is%20broken.%20And%20that's%20why%20we%20choose%20to%20cover%20things%20in%20a%20thematic%20way%20at%20ARK%20Invest%2C%20on%20a%20technology%20basis%2C%26quot%3B%20Keeney%20said%20in%20an%20interview%20with%20Business%20Insider.%20Placing%20a%20company%20like%20SpaceX%20or%20Tesla%20under%20an%20analyst%20solely%20focused%20on%20telecomm%20companies%20or%20automakers%20is%20too%20limiting%2C%20Keeney%20said%2C%20who%20reiterated%20Wood's%20point%20about%20companies%2C%20especially%20Musk's%2C%20converging%20into%20something%20bigger%20than%20the%20markets%20have%20ever%20seen%20before.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20why%20Wood%20has%20always%20been%20a%20big%20supporter%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcathie-wood-pick-tesla-if-only-invest-one-stock-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMusk's%20vision%20at%20Tesla%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20now%20SpaceX.%20The%20world's%20richest%20man%20has%20often%20blurred%20the%20lines%20between%20traditional%20sectors%20at%20his%20companies%2C%20which%20has%20both%20frustrated%20and%20thrilled%20investors.%20Greengold%20noted%20that%20Wood's%20backing%20of%20Musk%20dates%20back%20to%20her%20days%20at%20AllianceBernstein%2C%20when%20she%20was%20a%20Tesla%20investor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEquity%20capital%20is%20perpetual%20capital.%20Equity%20capital%20should%20be%20interested%20in%20the%20long%20term%2C%20literally%20the%20infinite%20interest%20of%20the%20business%2C%20not%20the%20quarterly%20interest.%20And%20so%20ARK%2C%20from%20its%20start%2C%20has%20focused%20on%20the%20long-term%20returns%20of%20businesses%2C%26quot%3B%20Winton%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20steadfast%20belief%20in%20their%20bets%20is%20one%20of%20the%20reasons%20Morningstar%20is%20iffy%20on%20the%20firm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGreengold%20said%20there%20%26quot%3Bcontinues%20to%20be%20concerns%20about%20ARK's%20approach%20to%20risk%20management%2C%26quot%3B%20though%20the%20hiring%20of%20a%20chief%20risk%20officer%20last%20year%20%E2%80%94%20Dan%20Rodriguez%2C%20who%20previously%20worked%20at%20hedge%20funds%20like%20P.%20Schoenfeld%20and%20Point72%20%E2%80%94%20is%20a%20positive%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20way%2C%20these%20worries%20about%20ARK's%20risk%20management%20echo%20what%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fshould-i-buy-spacex-ipo-investing-advice-elon-musk-spcx-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Einvestors%20have%20said%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20Musk's%20leadership%20style.%20Both%20Wood%20and%20Musk%20have%20stressed%20to%20skeptics%20and%20critics%20that%20they%20should%20trust%20the%20long-term%20vision%20during%20bouts%20of%20volatility.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20she%20and%20her%20deputies%20plan%20to%20help%20Musk%20push%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspacex-s1-filing-elon-musk-scifi-manifesto-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Escience-fiction-flavored%20worldview%3C%2Fa%3E%20out%20to%20the%20masses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe'll%20certainly%20be%20out%20there%20educating%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20on%20the%20livestream.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspacex-ipo-cathie-wood-ark-invest-elon-musk-2026-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1781169001000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a29c54c3b1b48ae08760036%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspacex-ipo-cathie-wood-ark-invest-elon-musk-2026-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22ARK%20Invest%20has%20been%20unwavering%20in%20its%20belief%20in%20volatile%20companies%20attempting%20to%20create%20new%20technologies.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22bsaacks%40businessinsider.com%20(Bradley%20Saacks)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I'm%20a%20billionaire%20hair%20care%20and%20tequila%20founder.%20I%20don't%20have%20an%20email%20address%20and%20am%20motivated%20by%20peace%20and%20love%20%E2%80%94%20here's%20my%20routine.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22John%20Paul%20DeJoria%20gives%20a%20peace%20sign%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a29a0d1a74097c573989525%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225400%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJohn%20Paul%20DeJoria.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20John%20Paul%20DeJoria%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20is%20an%20as-to