0how%20powerful%20leaders%20in%20business%20structure%20their%20workday.%20Reach%20out%20to%20editor%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fauthor%2Flauryn-haas%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELauryn%20Haas%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20share%20your%20daily%20routine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Faside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMy%20career%20inspired%20me%20to%20write%20my%20upcoming%20book%2C%20%26quot%3BSuccess%20Unshared%20Is%20Failure%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20autobiography%20cowritten%20with%20Mark%20Victor%20Hanson%2C%20to%20show%20how%20people%20can%20do%20this%20for%20themselves%20and%20find%20happiness%20in%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPeace%2C%20love%2C%20and%20happiness%20are%20what%20motivate%20me.%20That's%20my%20purpose%20on%20this%20planet.%20Throughout%20my%20day%2C%20I%20keep%20in%20mind%20that%20when%20you're%20kind%20to%20people%2C%20kindness%20comes%20right%20back%20to%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20what%20my%20typical%20day%20looks%20like.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227518745d-aac7-4191-83f7-75f536b533a8%5C%22%3EI%20usually%20wake%20up%20between%206%20and%207%3A30%20a.m.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20thing%20I'll%20do%20is%20drink%2015-20%20ounces%20of%20room-temperature%20water%20that%20has%20been%20sitting%20overnight.%20Hydration%20is%20a%20priority%20for%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20bathroom%2C%20I%20go%20directly%20back%20to%20bed%20for%20at%20least%20five%20minutes%2C%20sometimes%20longer%2C%20doing%20what%20I%20call%20present%20time.%20It's%20similar%20to%20meditation%2C%20where%20I%20try%20to%20clear%20my%20mind%20except%20for%20one%20thought%3A%20%26quot%3BThank%20you%2C%20creator%20of%20souls%2C%20for%20this%20incredible%20life%20of%20abundance.%20May%20joy%20stay%20with%20me%20throughout%20the%20day%2C%20for%20me%20to%20learn%20more%20each%20day%20as%20an%20observer%20without%20judgment%20of%20all%20my%20fellow%20humans.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20meditating%2C%20I%20spend%20about%20two%20minutes%20doing%2030%20perfect%20push-ups%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnavy-seal-shares-go-to-exercises-longevity-performance-minimal-equipment-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etechnique%20popularized%20by%20Navy%20SEALs%3C%2Fa%3E.%20That's%20my%20main%20exercise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20breakfast%2C%20I%20drink%20about%20half%20a%20cappuccino%20cup%20of%20regular%20coffee%20with%20biscotti.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20work%20from%20home%20daily%20when%20in%20town.%20After%20that%2C%20I%20make%20any%20necessary%20phone%20calls%20to%20my%20European%20businesses.%20Then%20I'll%20turn%20to%20the%20other%20businesses%20I'm%20involved%20with%2C%20along%20with%20my%20philanthropic%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224c910deb-e64e-49bf-99b0-530de4486d1f%5C%22%3EI%20don't%20have%20an%20email%20address%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20don't%20even%20own%20a%20computer.%20If%20needed%2C%20I'll%20use%20my%20assistant's%20computer.%20I'll%20either%20call%20you%20or%20write%20you%20a%20handwritten%20letter%20instead.%20I%20like%20that%20personal%20touch%3B%20it's%20old-fashioned%2C%20but%20it%20works%20for%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20lunch%2C%20I'll%20drink%20another%20glass%20of%20water%2C%20and%20I'll%20stop%20at%203%20p.m.%20to%20prevent%20sleep%20interruptions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20mostly%20eat%20at%20home%2C%20but%20I'll%20occasionally%20meet%20people%20in%20downtown%20Austin%20for%20lunch.%20We%20have%20a%20chef%2C%20whom%20I%20brought%20on%2017%20years%20ago%2C%20for%20my%20anniversary%20with%20my%20wife%2C%20Elaine.%20We're%20very%20fortunate.%20He%20cooks%20for%20us%20five%20days%20a%20week%20and%20usually%20sets%20food%20aside%20for%20the%20weekend.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223d58be14-6c25-43da-9574-e0dffe8e42d5%5C%22%3EI%20consider%20my%20blood%20type%20for%20meals%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmosquitoes-attracted-people-blood-type-beer-scent-2019-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EType%20O%20blood%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20I%20follow%20the%20blood-type%20diet%20philosophy.%20I've%20found%20that%20I%20do%20better%20when%20I%20eat%20some%20meat.%20I've%20tried%20to%20be%20a%20vegetarian%20before.%20I%20need%20meat%2C%20but%20everything%20in%20moderation.%20I%20always%20leave%20the%20table%20a%20little%20bit%20hungry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20lunch%2C%20I%20might%20spend%20time%20with%20my%20wife%20and%20grown%20kids%2C%20or%20I'll%20finish%20up%20business%20tasks%2C%20whether%20that's%20making%20phone%20calls%20or%20visiting%20the%20headquarters%20of%20my%20businesses%20in%20Austin.%20I'm%20helping%20to%20lead%20and%20advise%20Vendidit%20and%20GlobalSKU%20in%20their%20mission%20to%20streamline%20and%20optimize%20the%20resale%20and%20reverse%20logistics%20industries%20%E2%80%94%20including%20frequent%20calls%20with%20internal%20teams%20and%20industry%20experts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESometimes%20I'll%20go%20downtown%20to%20the%20entrepreneur%20center%20I%20started%20for%20the%20homeless%20to%20give%20lectures%20or%20serve%20food.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDinner%20from%20our%20chef%20might%20include%20vegetables%20like%20sweet%20potatoes%2C%20broccoli%2C%20or%20his%20delicious%20black-eyed%20peas%2C%20and%20for%20protein%2C%20we%20have%20fish%20or%20beef%20%E2%80%94%20organic%2C%20no%20antibiotics.%20I%20drink%20red%20wine%20about%20three%20times%20a%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224b5feab4-941f-4cf9-909c-6d157617586b%5C%22%3EAfter%20dinner%2C%20I'll%20stretch%20and%20take%20a%20moment%20to%20be%20thankful%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EEvening%20is%20an%20ideal%20time%20to%20call%20Asia%2C%20so%20I'll%20make%20any%20last%20business%20calls.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20wind%20down%2C%20we've%20been%20watching%20TV.%20We%20started%20watching%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgame-of-thrones-original-story-2017-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGame%20of%20Thrones%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20it%20had%20already%20ended%20and%20binged%20on%20three%20episodes%20a%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20nights%2C%20I%20might%20read.%20I%20enjoy%20reading%20books%20about%20self-help%20and%20spiritual%20books%20about%20the%20soul%2C%20the%20universe%2C%20how%20we%20ascend%2C%20and%20how%20our%20frequencies%20rise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a03fae8d-6947-4a3a-8c3d-ee0b42d75ee4%5C%22%3EBy%208%3A30%20or%209%20p.m.%2C%20the%20TV%20is%20off%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe're%20ready%20to%20go%20to%20bed%20by%2010%20p.m.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20I%20sleep%2C%20I%20say%20to%20myself%2C%20sometimes%20out%20loud%2C%20%26quot%3BThank%20you%2C%20creator%20of%20souls%2C%20for%20the%20joy%20in%20my%20life%20and%20for%20all%20the%20abundance%20I%20have.%20When%20something%20goes%20wrong%2C%20I%20remind%20myself%20it's%20only%20happening%20so%20I%20can%20learn%20from%20it%2C%20because%20I%20truly%20believe%20we're%20on%20this%20planet%20to%20learn.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPeople%20often%20ask%2C%20%26quot%3BWhat's%20the%20one%20thing%20you%20would%20change%20from%20the%20past%3F%26quot%3B%20My%20answer%20is%20nothing.%20I%20wouldn't%20change%20a%20thing%2C%20because%20everything%20that%20happened%20in%20my%20life%20brought%20me%20to%20where%20I%20am%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjohn-paul-dejoria-patron-tequila-haircare-power-hours-2026-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1781168701000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a29a716b19390180e4cfa26%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjohn-paul-dejoria-patron-tequila-haircare-power-hours-2026-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22John%20Paul%20DeJoria%20started%20John%20Paul%20Mitchell%20Systems%20in%201980%20while%20living%20in%20his%20car.%20He%20sold%20Patr%C3%B3n%20Tequila%20in%202018%20and%20is%20now%20a%20billionaire.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Kaila%20Yu)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2