EGA%2C%20most%20filled%20by%20women%20and%20young%20people.%20These%20roles%20extend%20beyond%20wages%2C%20involving%20environmental%20custodianship%20from%20land%20preparation%20to%20sapling%20care.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMGNREGA%20has%20been%20instrumental%20in%20bringing%20in%20local%20workers%20who%20not%20only%20earn%20but%20also%20develop%20a%20sense%20of%20responsibility%20towards%20the%20land.%20When%20someone%20helps%20raise%20a%20forest%20from%20scratch%2C%20it%20becomes%20personal%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Vishal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20watched%20young%20people%20grow%20into%20community%20leaders%20through%20this%20work.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20educate%20their%20neighbours%2C%20advocate%20for%20conservation%2C%20and%20carry%20the%20torch%20forward%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20sun%20sets%20over%20Rajinder%20Nagar%2C%20Inderjit%20walks%20slowly%20through%20his%20forest.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20the%20Punjab%20I%20remember%20as%20a%20child%20%E2%80%94%20lush%2C%20vibrant%2C%20alive.%20It%20is%20coming%20back%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20In%20Lang%2C%20Romanpreet%20watches%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F493007%2Fbutterfly-friendly-plants-for-indian-homes-marigold-hibiscus-tulsi%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebutterflies%20flit%20through%20the%20branches%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-09-04T201626.909_11zon-1756997217.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Billion%20Tree%20Project%20helps%20to%20plant%20trees%20and%20is%20a%20consistent%20source%20of%20livelihood%20for%20many%20villagers%2C%20especially%20women%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-09-04T201626.909_11zon-1756997217.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-09-04T201626.909_11zon-1756997217-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-09-04T201626.909_11zon-1756997217-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-09-04T201626.909_11zon-1756997217-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-09-04T201626.909_11zon-1756997217-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-496582%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20Billion%20Tree%20Project%20helps%20to%20plant%20trees%20and%20is%20a%20consistent%20source%20of%20livelihood%20for%20many%20villagers%2C%20especially%20women%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUltimately%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Billion%20Tree%20Project%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20not%20only%20about%20greening%20land%20but%20about%20rekindling%20identity%2C%20reviving%20community%2C%20and%20reimagining%20a%20future%20in%20harmony%20with%20nature.%20Gurpreet%20puts%20it%20aptly%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPlanting%20a%20tree%20is%20an%20act%20of%20faith%20in%20the%20future.%20It%20is%20a%20promise%20that%20we%20care%2C%20that%20we%20will%20nurture%2C%20and%20that%20we%20believe%20in%20the%20resilience%20of%20this%20land%20and%20its%20people.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAll%20pictures%20courtesy%20Roundglass%20Foundation%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1757215800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-09-04T195457.273_11zon-1756995925.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D496504%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Roundglass%20Foundation%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98The%20Billion%20Tree%20Project%E2%80%99%20has%20planted%20over%203%20million%20native%20trees%20across%20Punjab%2C%20restoring%20biodiversity%2C%20improving%20soil%20and%20water%20health%2C%20and%20creating%20thousands%20of%20jobs%20for%20women%20and%20youth.%20Learn%20how%20this%20movement%20is%20improving%20lives.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Raajwrita%20Dutta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F496504%2Froundglass-foundation-the-billion-tree-project-planting-native-trees-in-villages-livelihoods%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Farmer%20Turns%20Cashew%20Crop%20Ruined%20By%20Rains%20into%20Sprouts%2C%20Pickles%20%26amp%3B%20More%3B%20Earns%20Rs%2025%20Lakh%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20interviews%20and%20reporting%20for%20this%20story%20were%20conducted%20in%20September%202024.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20large%20produce%20of%20wet%2C%20harvested%20cashews%20was%20in%20front%20of%20Brijith%20Krishnan.%20The%20unseasonal%20rains%20in%20his%20hometown%20in%20Kerala%20had%20ruined%20the%20crop%20again.%20He%20knew%20this%20crop%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20fetch%20him%20any%20income.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAround%20the%20same%20time%20in%202020%2C%20the%20mechanical%20engineering%20diploma%20holder%20also%20faced%20another%20challenging%20turn%20of%20events%20when%20he%20unexpectedly%20lost%20his%20job%20as%20a%20supervisor%20in%20an%20IT%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ca%20data-tracker%3D%5C%22%7B%26quot%3Barticle_name%26quot%3B%3A%26quot%3BArticle%20Page%20Ad%20Banner%26quot%3B%2C%26quot%3Bposition%26quot%3B%3A1%2C%26quot%3Barticle_id%26quot%3B%3A496857%7D%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22http